// © heelandy
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// HIGHSTRIKE V44 — V43 hardened (integrity fixes; backtest now measures real dollars).
//  2.1 FILLS: commission.cash_per_order 0.52 + slippage 2 ticks (was percent 0.0 / slip 0).
//  2.2 MACRO STAND-DOWN: hard-gate longs vs confirmed SPY downtrend, shorts vs uptrend
//       (input macro_standdown, default ON). Closes the 2022 long-in-downtrend hole.
//  2.4 CONFLUENCE: entry was OR-of-5 reclaims; now VWAP+EMA both (input trig_confluence).
//  2.3 TRIGGER STOP: input stop_anchor "Trigger-relative" anchors the stop to the nearest
//       active VWAP/EMA (flows through risk/sizing/TP/RR). Default "Structure" (opt-in, A/B in Phase 3).
//  2.5 DEAD CODE: removed orphaned reaction-at-level layer + cosmetic preset system (-7 dead inputs).
//  2.7 SIZING: fixed qty default 1->2 (TP1-scale runner not inert); eval guardrails available (eval_on).
//  2.8 SESSIONS: "HS Windows" preset (0930-1000,1030-1130,1330-1530) + EOD-flat (disciplined mode).
//  2.9 PARITY: long/short audited symmetric. TODO: 2.6 deeper input prune (158 inputs).
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// HIGHSTRIKE V43 — V39 with MULTIPLE VWAP/EMA in the entry triggers (the only change).
//  VWAP trigger now reacts to 2 anchors (session + weekly); EMA trigger reacts to 3 EMAs (9/20/50).
//  The combination entry (zone / retest / VWAP / EMA / sweep / cons) and everything else is UNCHANGED
//  from V39. Long & short remain symmetric (long_signals_on / short_signals_on).
// HIGHSTRIKE V38 STRATEGY — V37 + opt-in engine: structure-trail & CHoCH exit (strategy), HTF entry gate, per-trigger stops (strategy), trigger-quality gate, multi-degree structure, zone freshness, configurable bias weights. Defaults preserve V37.
//  Same signal engine as the indicator; adds real order execution so the TradingView
//  Strategy Tester produces actual PF / equity / drawdown / win-rate / per-grade stats.
//  V26: volume now read directionally — confirm when it agrees with trend, WAIT when it opposes.
//  V23: TP/SL geometry hardened (entry stays near price; degenerate geometry blocked).
//  V24: RR gate now uses PLANNED RR from the latched entry (not drifting close) + 24/7 session toggle.
//  V25: dashboard computed once/bar (load speed); dead var removed; min stop-distance floor; bias N-bar confirm.
//  CHANGE 1  Entry latched to a FIXED structural zone level (no more drift with price).
//  CHANGE 2  Multi-TF demand/supply zones (5/15/30/1h/4h) via security floats — every
//            higher TF than chart stacks, 4h always shown.
//  CHANGE 3  Latched entry anchors to the strongest nearby MTF zone (confluence).
//  CHANGE 4  Massive Zones loosened (msz_loose) so demand/supply boxes appear more often.
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// UNDERLYING FIX vs all prior versions:
//  The directional decision is now ONE symmetric bias spine (HTF + EMA + DMI),
//  computed once. Long and short are mirror expressions of the SAME bias, so a
//  LONG bias can never coexist with a downtrend. The lagging structure state
//  machine is demoted to confirmation/display — it no longer drives firing.
// TWO LAYERS:
//  ACCURACY (always on, objective): master_bias, setup direction, grade, sweep,
//   zone, HTF — the honest market read, never suppressed by user prefs.
//  TIMING (user toggles, discretionary): session/cooldown/macro/RR/cap decide
//   whether an accurate setup actually FIRES. Dashboard shows why one didn't.
// TREND-AWARE FLOOR: with-bias setups fire at B (floor_with); counter-bias
//  setups require A (floor_counter). Set per-direction, live-toggleable.
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// FIXES vs V20:
//  F1 Direction gates restored — momentum veto + master EMA trend filter + live-break gate
//     (stops longs firing on downtrend bounces; lets shorts fire on close-break of pivot)
//  F2 open_positions decrement moved into CB resolution block (was locking after 2 trades/day)
//  F3 HTF bundle: removed close[1] double-lag, EMAs and close now consistent
//  F4 vol_ma: robust 20-bar volume MA (na-injection version silently broke vol_confirm)
//  F5 PDH/PDL bundled into ONE request.security; removed unused pdc
//  F6 Heavy label blocks guarded with barstate.isconfirmed
// ENHANCEMENTS:
//  Trend-aware floor: B with bias, A counter-bias (floor_with / floor_counter)
//  E2 ⚡ Toggles group: Long/Short/Momentum/Trend/Live-break/HTF/Divergence/Massive Zones
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

//@version=6
// V44 FILL REALISM (#1 integrity fix): real costs so PF targets dollars, not paper.
//  cash_per_order is charged per fill. MNQ round-turn ~$0.74–1.04 ≈ 2 orders -> ~0.52/order
//  (scaling out at TP1 adds a 3rd order, slightly conservative). slippage 2 ticks (1–3 range).
//  Tune commission_value per instrument (MNQ ~0.52, NQ ~2.0, MES ~0.52, ES ~2.0).
strategy("HIGHSTRIKE V44 STRATEGY", overlay=true,
     max_boxes_count=300, max_labels_count=300, max_lines_count=200,
     initial_capital=100000, pyramiding=0,
     default_qty_type=strategy.fixed, default_qty_value=1,
     commission_type=strategy.commission.cash_per_order, commission_value=0.52,
     slippage=2, process_orders_on_close=true)

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// ⚡ TOGGLES
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
long_signals_on  = input.bool(true, "LONG Signals",   group="⚡ Toggles", inline="t1")
short_signals_on = input.bool(true, "SHORT Signals",  group="⚡ Toggles", inline="t1")
momo_en          = input.bool(true, "Momentum veto",  group="⚡ Toggles", inline="t2")
trendfilter_en   = input.bool(true, "Trend filter",   group="⚡ Toggles", inline="t2")
livebreak_en     = input.bool(true, "Live-break gate",group="⚡ Toggles", inline="t3")
htf_en           = input.bool(true, "HTF bias",       group="⚡ Toggles", inline="t3")
div_en           = input.bool(true, "Divergence pen", group="⚡ Toggles", inline="t4")
msz_en           = input.bool(true, "Massive Zones",  group="⚡ Toggles", inline="t4")

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// TICKER + ASSET CLASS
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
string raw_ticker = str.upper(syminfo.ticker)

bool is_metal_fut    = str.contains(raw_ticker,"MGC") or str.contains(raw_ticker,"GC") or
                       str.contains(raw_ticker,"SI")  or str.contains(raw_ticker,"PL")
bool is_energy_fut   = str.contains(raw_ticker,"MCL") or str.contains(raw_ticker,"CL") or
                       str.contains(raw_ticker,"NG")  or str.contains(raw_ticker,"RB")
bool is_currency_fut = str.contains(raw_ticker,"M6E") or str.contains(raw_ticker,"6E") or
                       str.contains(raw_ticker,"M6B") or str.contains(raw_ticker,"6B") or
                       str.contains(raw_ticker,"6J")  or str.contains(raw_ticker,"DX")
bool is_index_fut    = str.contains(raw_ticker,"MNQ") or str.contains(raw_ticker,"MES") or
                       str.contains(raw_ticker,"NQ")  or str.contains(raw_ticker,"ES")  or
                       str.contains(raw_ticker,"MYM") or str.contains(raw_ticker,"YM")  or
                       str.contains(raw_ticker,"M2K") or str.contains(raw_ticker,"RTY")

string asset_class       = syminfo.type == "futures" ? "FUTURE" : "EQUITY"   // robust: any futures contract
string asset_macro_class = is_metal_fut ? "METAL" : is_energy_fut ? "ENERGY" :
                           is_currency_fut ? "CURRENCY" : "EQUITY_INDEX"

string ticker_class =
     str.contains(raw_ticker,"NVDA")  ? "NVDA"    : str.contains(raw_ticker,"TSLA")  ? "TSLA"    :
     str.contains(raw_ticker,"AAPL")  ? "AAPL"    : str.contains(raw_ticker,"MSFT")  ? "MSFT"    :
     str.contains(raw_ticker,"GOOGL") or str.contains(raw_ticker,"GOOG") ? "GOOGL"                :
     str.contains(raw_ticker,"META")  ? "META"    : str.contains(raw_ticker,"AMZN")  ? "AMZN"    :
     str.contains(raw_ticker,"AVGO")  ? "AVGO"    : str.contains(raw_ticker,"ORCL")  ? "ORCL"    :
     str.contains(raw_ticker,"AMD")   ? "AMD"     : str.contains(raw_ticker,"NFLX")  ? "NFLX"    :
     str.contains(raw_ticker,"SPY")   ? "SPY"     : str.contains(raw_ticker,"QQQ")   ? "QQQ"     :
     str.contains(raw_ticker,"IWM")   ? "IWM"     : str.contains(raw_ticker,"MNQ")   ? "MNQ_FUT" :
     str.contains(raw_ticker,"NQ")    ? "NQ_FUT"  : str.contains(raw_ticker,"MES")   ? "MES_FUT" :
     str.contains(raw_ticker,"ES")    ? "ES_FUT"  : str.contains(raw_ticker,"MYM")   ? "MYM_FUT" :
     str.contains(raw_ticker,"YM")    ? "YM_FUT"  : str.contains(raw_ticker,"M2K")   ? "M2K_FUT" :
     str.contains(raw_ticker,"RTY")   ? "RTY_FUT" : "GENERIC"

float ticker_sl_mult =
     ticker_class == "NVDA"    ? 1.3 : ticker_class == "TSLA"    ? 1.5 :
     ticker_class == "AAPL"    ? 1.0 : ticker_class == "MSFT"    ? 1.0 :
     ticker_class == "GOOGL"   ? 1.1 : ticker_class == "META"    ? 1.2 :
     ticker_class == "AMZN"    ? 1.2 : ticker_class == "AVGO"    ? 1.2 :
     ticker_class == "ORCL"    ? 1.0 : ticker_class == "AMD"     ? 1.4 :
     ticker_class == "NFLX"    ? 1.3 : ticker_class == "SPY"     ? 0.9 :
     ticker_class == "QQQ"     ? 1.0 : ticker_class == "IWM"     ? 1.1 :
     ticker_class == "MNQ_FUT" ? 1.0 : ticker_class == "NQ_FUT"  ? 1.0 :
     ticker_class == "MES_FUT" ? 1.2 : ticker_class == "ES_FUT"  ? 1.2 : 1.2

float ticker_pt_val = syminfo.pointvalue   // authoritative per-contract $ value (works for any future/asset)

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// INPUTS
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
macro_en          = input.bool(true,  "MACRO REGIME filter ON",      group="Macro Regime")
macro_auto_ref    = input.bool(true,  "Auto-select macro per asset",  group="Macro Regime")
macro_spy_sym     = input.symbol("SPY",      "Equity macro ref",      group="Macro Regime")
macro_vix_sym     = input.symbol("CBOE:VIX", "Equity vol",            group="Macro Regime")
macro_dxy_sym     = input.symbol("TVC:DXY",  "DXY",                   group="Macro Regime")
macro_gld_sym     = input.symbol("AMEX:GLD", "Gold ref",              group="Macro Regime")
macro_uso_sym     = input.symbol("AMEX:USO", "Oil ref",               group="Macro Regime")
macro_ovx_sym     = input.symbol("CBOE:OVX", "Oil VIX",               group="Macro Regime")
macro_vix_calm    = input.float(15.0, "VIX calm",     group="Macro Regime", step=1, minval=8,  maxval=30)
macro_vix_volatile= input.float(25.0, "VIX volatile", group="Macro Regime", step=1, minval=15, maxval=40)
macro_vix_extreme = input.float(35.0, "VIX extreme",  group="Macro Regime", step=1, minval=25, maxval=80)
macro_spy_adx_min = input.float(25.0, "Macro ADX min",group="Macro Regime", step=1, minval=15, maxval=40)
macro_persist_n   = input.int(3,  "Persistence bars (base)",    group="Macro Regime", minval=1, maxval=10,
                   tooltip="C→A transition uses 2× this value. D always immediate.")
macro_block_d     = input.bool(true, "BLOCK trades in REGIME D", group="Macro Regime")
macro_only_a_in_c = input.bool(true, "Only A+ in REGIME C",     group="Macro Regime")
macro_block_b_rng = input.bool(true, "Block trend in REGIME B",  group="Macro Regime")
macro_override    = input.bool(false,"Override macro",           group="Macro Regime")
macro_override_to = input.string("A","Force regime to:", group="Macro Regime", options=["A","B","C","D"])
macro_standdown   = input.bool(true, "Macro stand-down vs SPY trend (V44)", group="Macro Regime", tooltip="V44 fix for the 2022 hole. HARD-GATES longs while SPY is in a confirmed daily downtrend (close<EMA20<EMA50) and shorts while confirmed uptrend. Previously spy_downtrend only added a +1 grade bonus and never blocked. Fails open if the macro ref has no data.")

struct_lb_fix  = input.int(5,     "Pivot lookback",    group="Structure", minval=2, maxval=20)
struct_adaptive= input.bool(true, "Adaptive lookback", group="Structure")
struct_tol_pct = input.float(0.10,"Pivot tolerance %", group="Structure", step=0.05, minval=0.0, maxval=2.0)
struct_show    = input.bool(true, "Show HH/HL/LL/LH",  group="Structure")
struct_show_bos= input.bool(true, "Show BOS/CHoCH",    group="Structure")
// F1 directional controls
momo_thresh    = input.float(0.3, "Momentum threshold (ATR units)", group="Structure", step=0.05, minval=0.1, maxval=2.0)
trend_ema_f_in = input.int(21,    "Trend filter EMA fast", group="Structure", minval=5)
trend_ema_s_in = input.int(50,    "Trend filter EMA slow", group="Structure", minval=20)
trend_show     = input.bool(true, "Plot trend EMA",        group="Structure")

floor_with     = input.int(6, "Floor: WITH bias (B)",     group="Scoring", minval=4, maxval=12,
                 tooltip="Setups aligned with master bias fire at/above this (default 6 = B).")
floor_counter  = input.int(9, "Floor: COUNTER bias (A)",  group="Scoring", minval=6, maxval=12,
                 tooltip="Counter-bias setups need this (default 9 = A). Bias NONE also uses this.")
bias_confirm_bars = input.int(2, "Bias confirm bars", group="Scoring", minval=1, maxval=10,
                 tooltip="Master bias must persist this many bars before it flips (anti-whipsaw at regime edges). 1 = instant (original behavior).")

local_adx_min  = input.float(20.0,"Local ADX min",    group="Local Regime", step=1, minval=15, maxval=35)
local_atr_hi   = input.float(2.5, "Volatile ATR%",    group="Local Regime", step=0.25, minval=1.0, maxval=10.0)
local_block_rng= input.bool(true, "BLOCK in RANGE",   group="Local Regime")
local_block_vol= input.bool(false,"BLOCK in VOLATILE", group="Local Regime")

sweep_en          = input.bool(true,  "Sweep detection",                    group="Sweep")
sweep_depth_atr   = input.float(0.3,  "Sweep depth × ATR",                  group="Sweep", step=0.1, minval=0.1, maxval=2.0)
sweep_show_contra = input.bool(true,  "Show contra-structure sweeps (gray)", group="Sweep")
sweep_show_level  = input.bool(true,  "Draw swept level line",               group="Sweep")

ob_body_min    = input.float(0.3, "OB body min × ATR", group="Zones", step=0.1, minval=0.1)
ob_max         = input.int(5,     "Max OBs tracked",   group="Zones", minval=2, maxval=10)
fvg_max        = input.int(8,     "Max FVGs tracked",  group="Zones", minval=2, maxval=20)
zone_stale_atr = input.float(3.0, "Zone stale × ATR",  group="Zones", step=0.5, minval=1.0)
msz_max        = input.int(3,     "Max Massive Zones", group="Zones", minval=1, maxval=5)

htf_dynamic    = input.bool(true, "Dynamic HTF",  group="HTF")
htf_manual     = input.timeframe("D","Manual HTF", group="HTF")
htf_ema_fast   = input.int(50,  "HTF EMA fast",   group="HTF", minval=10)
htf_ema_slow   = input.int(200, "HTF EMA slow",   group="HTF", minval=50)

vc_en          = input.bool(true,  "Volume confirm for A+",           group="Volume")
vc_mult        = input.float(1.5,  "Vol confirm mult",                group="Volume", step=0.1, minval=1.0, maxval=3.0)
vol_color_bars = input.bool(true,  "Color candles by volume type",    group="Volume")
vol_show_labels= input.bool(true,  "Show volume event labels",        group="Volume")
vol_climax_mult= input.float(2.0,  "Climax threshold (× vol MA)",     group="Volume", step=0.1, minval=1.2, maxval=5.0)
vol_absorb_mult= input.float(1.5,  "Absorption threshold (× vol MA)", group="Volume", step=0.1, minval=1.0, maxval=3.0)
vol_div_pct    = input.float(15.0, "Divergence threshold %",          group="Volume", step=5.0, minval=5.0, maxval=40.0)
voldir_mode    = input.string("Require confirming", "Vol-direction gate", options=["Off", "Veto opposing", "Require confirming"], group="Volume", tooltip="Off = volume does not gate firing. Veto opposing = block a long only when sellers clearly dominate (short when buyers do). Require confirming = a long fires ONLY when buyers dominate the bar (short only when sellers do). NOTE: buyer/seller split is a candle-direction proxy, not true tick delta.")
entry_market   = input.bool(true,  "STRATEGY: market entry (else limit at zone)", group="Strategy", tooltip="Market (default) fills at signal-bar close — guarantees the signal becomes a trade. Limit rests at the latched entry and only fills on a retest (tests fill realism, fewer fills).")
strat_fixed_qty = input.int(2, "STRATEGY: fixed qty (0 = risk-based)", group="Strategy", minval=0, tooltip="Contracts/shares per trade. V44 default 2 so the TP1 50%-scale + runner is NOT inert (1 contract can't split). 1 collapses the two-target exit. 0 = risk-based from Max risk $ / eval risk (set realistically or futures will not size).")

pat_en   = input.bool(true, "Morning/Evening Star", group="Patterns")
pat_show = input.bool(true, "Show pattern labels",  group="Patterns")

sl_buf_atr   = input.float(0.3,    "SL buffer × ATR",   group="Risk", step=0.1,  minval=0.1, maxval=2.0)
sl_max_atr   = input.float(2.5,    "SL max × ATR cap",  group="Risk", step=0.25, minval=1.0, maxval=5.0)
min_stop_atr = input.float(0.5,    "Min stop distance × ATR", group="Risk", step=0.1, minval=0.1, maxval=2.0, tooltip="Floor on stop distance so TP1/TP2 are not absurdly tight and sizing stays sane. Stop is clamped to >= this and <= SL max cap.")
stop_anchor  = input.string("Structure", "Stop anchor (V44 2.3)", options=["Structure","Trigger-relative"], group="Risk", tooltip="Structure = original (zone/sweep/pivot — can sit far from a VWAP/EMA-triggered entry). Trigger-relative = anchor the stop to the nearest active VWAP/EMA the entry reclaims, so stop distance tracks the trigger (flows through risk/sizing/TP/RR coherently). Default OFF pending Phase-3 A/B validation; for this VWAP/EMA-only engine it is the more coherent choice.")
tp1_rr       = input.float(1.0,    "TP1 RR",            group="Risk", step=0.25, minval=0.5, maxval=3.0)
tp2_rr       = input.float(2.0,    "TP2 RR",            group="Risk", step=0.25, minval=1.0, maxval=10.0)
tp1_pct       = input.int(50, "Exit: TP1 close %", group="Exit Management", minval=10, maxval=100, step=5, tooltip="Percent closed at TP1; remainder is the runner.")
after_tp1     = input.string("BE", "Exit: runner stop after TP1", options=["BE", "BE + lock", "Keep original SL", "Trail (ATR)", "Trail (structure)"], group="Exit Management", tooltip="What the runner stop does once TP1 fills. BE = move to entry (current behavior). Keep original SL / Trail give the runner room to capture bigger winners (fixes winners < losers).")
be_lock_rr    = input.float(0.3, "Exit: BE+lock RR", group="Exit Management", step=0.1, minval=0.0, maxval=2.0, tooltip="For 'BE + lock': lock this fraction of initial risk as profit on the runner stop.")
trail_atr     = input.float(2.0, "Exit: trail distance x ATR", group="Exit Management", step=0.25, minval=0.5, tooltip="For 'Trail (ATR)': runner stop trails price by this many ATR.")
runner_target = input.string("Fixed TP2", "Exit: runner target", options=["Fixed TP2", "None (ride trail)"], group="Exit Management", tooltip="Fixed TP2 caps the runner; None lets it ride the trailing stop with no cap.")
exit_on_choch = input.bool(false, "Exit: close on opposing CHoCH", group="Exit Management", tooltip="Close the position when structure flips against it (bearish CHoCH while long / bullish CHoCH while short).")
min_rr       = input.float(1.5,    "Min RR to fire (vs close)",group="Risk", step=0.25, minval=0.5, maxval=5.0)
max_risk_dlr = input.float(100.0,  "Max risk $",        group="Risk", step=25,   minval=10)

// ===== L18 — Prop Eval Guardrails (opt-in; off = unchanged V38 behavior) =====
eval_on            = input.bool(false, "EVAL: enable prop guardrails", group="Prop Eval", tooltip="Sizes to a fixed $ risk with a contract floor, halts NEW entries on a daily loss limit, and halts within a buffer of the trailing drawdown. Off = unchanged behavior.")
eval_risk_dlr      = input.float(150.0, "EVAL: risk $ per trade",      group="Prop Eval", step=25, minval=25)
eval_min_contracts = input.int(2,       "EVAL: min contracts (runner floor)", group="Prop Eval", minval=1, tooltip="Floor so the runner is not inert; the validated exit lever needs >=2 units.")
daily_loss_limit   = input.float(600.0, "EVAL: daily loss halt $",     group="Prop Eval", step=50, minval=50)
trail_dd           = input.float(1500.0,"EVAL: trailing drawdown $",   group="Prop Eval", step=100, minval=100)
trail_buffer       = input.float(300.0, "EVAL: trailing halt buffer $",group="Prop Eval", step=50, minval=0)
float eff_risk_dlr = eval_on ? eval_risk_dlr : max_risk_dlr
max_pos_dlr  = input.float(5000.0, "Max position $",    group="Risk", step=500,  minval=100)
max_open_pos = input.int(2,        "Max concurrent positions", group="Risk", minval=1, maxval=5)

cb_en        = input.bool(true,   "Daily stop CB",     group="Circuit Breaker")
cb_max_losses= input.int(3,       "Max consec losses", group="Circuit Breaker", minval=2, maxval=10)
cb_daily_dlr = input.float(300.0, "Max daily loss $",  group="Circuit Breaker", step=50,  minval=50)

sess_on      = input.bool(true,  "Session filter ON",   group="Sessions")
sess_anytime = input.bool(true,  "Allow session ANY time (24/7)", group="Sessions", tooltip="Overrides preset/window entirely — session counts as active at all times, including lunch/open/close skips. Use for 24h futures or testing.")
sess_filter  = input.string("RTH Only","Session preset", group="Sessions",
               options=["RTH Only","HS Windows","Morning","Afternoon","Late Day","Power Hour","Custom","Futures All","Futures NY"])
custom_sess  = input.session("0930-1130,1330-1500","Custom session", group="Sessions")
sess_tz      = input.string("America/New_York","Timezone", group="Sessions",
               options=["America/New_York","America/Chicago","Europe/London"])
avoid_lunch  = input.bool(true, "Avoid 11:30-13:30", group="Sessions")
avoid_open15 = input.bool(true, "Skip first 15 min", group="Sessions")
avoid_close15= input.bool(true, "Skip last 15 min",  group="Sessions")
eod_flat     = input.bool(true, "EOD: flatten at session end (V44 2.8)", group="Sessions", tooltip="No overnight risk. Closes any open position once per day at the EOD time below. Active only in disciplined/windowed mode (Session filter ON and 24/7 OFF) — so it does not disturb 24/7 validation runs.")
eod_hhmm     = input.int(1558, "EOD flatten time HHMM (ET)", group="Sessions", minval=0, maxval=2359, tooltip="Local-exchange time (sess_tz) to force-flat, e.g. 1558 = 15:58. Set before your RTH close / last window end.")

earnings_blackout = input.bool(false,"Earnings blackout", group="Event Blackout")
event_blackout    = input.bool(false,"Event blackout",    group="Event Blackout")

cd_auto        = input.bool(true, "Auto cooldown (adapts to timeframe)", group="Timing")
cd_bars_manual = input.int(3, "Manual cooldown bars (when auto OFF)", group="Timing", minval=0, maxval=100)

show_pdh_pdl   = input.bool(true, "Show PDH/PDL lines",        group="Display")
show_or        = input.bool(true, "Show Opening Range (30m)",  group="Display")
show_zones     = input.bool(true, "Show OB/FVG boxes",         group="Display")
show_levels    = input.bool(true, "Show entry/SL/TP lines",    group="Display")
show_dollars   = input.bool(true, "Show $ on signals",         group="Display")
show_dashboard = input.bool(true, "Show dashboard",            group="Display")
show_macro_bg  = input.bool(true, "Macro regime background",   group="Display")

mtf_show       = input.bool(true, "Show MTF demand/supply zones",  group="MTF Zones")
mtf_body_min   = input.float(0.3, "MTF OB body min x ATR",         group="MTF Zones", step=0.1, minval=0.1)
entry_near_atr = input.float(0.4, "Entry: at-zone distance x ATR",  group="Entry Anchor", step=0.05, minval=0.1, tooltip="How close price must be to a zone EDGE to anchor entry (retest). Tighter = more surgical. 0.4 ATR is tight; raise toward 1.5 for looser entries.")
entry_mode     = input.string("Hybrid", "Entry mode", options=["Momentum", "Surgical", "Hybrid"], group="Entry Anchor", tooltip="Momentum = fire on setup (looser, validated baseline). Surgical = require a reaction candle at a zone AND only one entry per structural leg. Hybrid = require the reaction candle but no one-shot lockout.")
// V44 2.5/2.6: react_wick input removed (only fed the deleted reaction-at-level layer).

trig_vwap_m    = input.bool(true,  "Trigger: VWAP pullback + reclaim",     group="Entry Triggers")
trig_ema_m     = input.bool(true,  "Trigger: EMA20/50 pullback + reclaim", group="Entry Triggers")
use_vwap2      = input.bool(true,  "VWAP trigger: react to 2 anchors (session + weekly)", group="Entry Triggers", tooltip="Multiple VWAP. The VWAP pullback+reclaim trigger fires off the session VWAP OR the weekly VWAP.")
use_ema3       = input.bool(true,  "EMA trigger: react to 3 EMAs (9 / 20 / 50)", group="Entry Triggers", tooltip="Multiple EMA. The EMA pullback+reclaim trigger fires off the 9, 20, OR 50 EMA — catches shallow (9) through deep (50) pullbacks.")
trig_cons_m    = input.bool(false, "Trigger: consolidation break",         group="Entry Triggers")
trig_confluence= input.string("VWAP+EMA (both)", "Entry confluence (V44)", options=["Any (OR)","VWAP+EMA (both)",">=2 triggers"], group="Entry Triggers", tooltip="V44 fix for trade inflation. Any = original OR-of-5 reclaims (any one fires). VWAP+EMA = require BOTH a VWAP reclaim AND an EMA reclaim on the bar. >=2 = at least two of {VWAP, EMA, cons} agree. V44 default tightens to VWAP+EMA.")

// V44 2.5/2.6: cosmetic Per-TF Auto Combo preset system removed (auto_tf_combo + preset_5m..4h fed
//  only the dashboard label, never the triggers — V43 already forced triggers to VWAP/EMA).

per_tf_stop    = input.bool(false, "Per-TF stop cap (x ATR)", group="Per-TF Stop", tooltip="ON = cap the stop distance with the chart timeframe value below, so each TF's max drawdown stays in target.")
stopcap_5m     = input.float(1.0, "<=5m stop cap x ATR",  group="Per-TF Stop", step=0.1, minval=0.2)
stopcap_15m    = input.float(1.2, "<=15m stop cap x ATR", group="Per-TF Stop", step=0.1, minval=0.2)
stopcap_30m    = input.float(1.5, "<=30m stop cap x ATR", group="Per-TF Stop", step=0.1, minval=0.2)
stopcap_1h     = input.float(2.0, "<=1h stop cap x ATR",  group="Per-TF Stop", step=0.1, minval=0.2)
stopcap_4h     = input.float(2.5, ">1h stop cap x ATR",   group="Per-TF Stop", step=0.1, minval=0.2)
cons_len       = input.int(6,      "Consolidation lookback (bars)",        group="Entry Triggers", minval=3)
cons_mult      = input.float(1.2,  "Consolidation max range x ATR",        group="Entry Triggers", step=0.1, minval=0.3)

// ===== V37 component upgrades (opt-in; defaults preserve V36 behavior) =====
string vwap_anchor   = input.string("Session", "VWAP anchor", options=["Session","Weekly","Monthly"], group="V37 Upgrades", tooltip="Session = prior behavior. Weekly/Monthly make VWAP meaningful on 4h/Daily.")
bool   cons_vol_filt = input.bool(true,  "Consolidation: require volume > avg", group="V37 Upgrades", tooltip="Only fire a consolidation break when volume exceeds its 20-bar average. Affects only the consolidation trigger.")
bool   eqhl_on       = input.bool(false, "Mark equal highs/lows (liquidity)", group="V37 Upgrades", tooltip="Tags clusters of equal swing highs/lows (stop pools).")
float  eqhl_tol      = input.float(0.1,  "Equal H/L tolerance %", group="V37 Upgrades", step=0.05, minval=0.01, maxval=1.0)
bool   rvol_gate     = input.bool(false, "Gate entries by relative volume", group="V37 Upgrades", tooltip="When on, a trigger fires only if relative volume (vs 20-bar avg) >= the minimum below.")
float  rvol_min      = input.float(1.0,  "Min relative volume", group="V37 Upgrades", step=0.1, minval=0.5, maxval=3.0)

// ===== V38 engine upgrades (opt-in; defaults preserve V37 behavior) =====
bool   htf_gate_on   = input.bool(false, "HTF gate: filter entries by higher TF", group="HTF Gate", tooltip="When on, the higher-TF overlay (HTF Signal group) blocks counter-trend entries instead of only displaying.")
string htf_gate_mode = input.string("Block opposite", "HTF gate mode", options=["Block opposite","Require aligned"], group="HTF Gate", tooltip="Block opposite = no longs when HTF bearish / no shorts when HTF bullish. Require aligned = longs only when HTF bullish, shorts only when HTF bearish.")
bool   trigq_gate    = input.bool(false, "Trigger quality: gate by min score", group="Trigger Quality", tooltip="Quality 0-5 = volume confirm + at-zone + structure aligned + HTF aligned + high rel-volume. When on, a setup fires only if quality >= the minimum.")
int    trigq_min     = input.int(2, "Min trigger quality (0-5)", group="Trigger Quality", minval=0, maxval=5)
bool   mdeg_on       = input.bool(false, "Multi-degree: compute higher swing degree", group="Multi-Degree", tooltip="Adds a second, slower swing degree (larger pivot lookback) for trend context.")
int    mdeg_lb       = input.int(15, "Higher-degree pivot lookback", group="Multi-Degree", minval=8)
bool   mdeg_gate     = input.bool(false, "Multi-degree gate: require degree agreement", group="Multi-Degree", tooltip="When on, longs are blocked while the higher degree is a downtrend, shorts while it is an uptrend.")
bool   zone_mitig    = input.bool(false, "Zone freshness: skip mitigated zones", group="Zone Mitigation", tooltip="When on, a zone trigger fires only if price has not already traded through the zone within the lookback (heuristic freshness).")
int    mitig_lb      = input.int(10, "Zone freshness lookback (bars)", group="Zone Mitigation", minval=2)
int    w_htf         = input.int(2, "Bias weight: HTF", group="Bias Weights", minval=0, maxval=4, tooltip="Direction-spine weights. Defaults 2/2/1 with threshold 2 reproduce prior behavior.")
int    w_trend       = input.int(2, "Bias weight: EMA trend", group="Bias Weights", minval=0, maxval=4)
int    w_dmi         = input.int(1, "Bias weight: DMI", group="Bias Weights", minval=0, maxval=4)
int    bias_thresh   = input.int(2, "Bias threshold (|score| >=)", group="Bias Weights", minval=1, maxval=6)
bool   pertrig_stops = input.bool(false, "Per-trigger stops: scale stop by trigger", group="Per-Trigger Stops", tooltip="Tighten stops for level triggers (retest/sweep/zone), widen for momentum triggers (VWAP/EMA). Applied at entry, so realized RR may differ from the gate.")
float  sl_mult_tight = input.float(0.8, "Tight stop x (retest/sweep/zone)", group="Per-Trigger Stops", step=0.05, minval=0.3, maxval=1.5)
float  sl_mult_wide  = input.float(1.3, "Wide stop x (VWAP/EMA)", group="Per-Trigger Stops", step=0.05, minval=0.8, maxval=2.5)
bool   time_stop_on   = input.bool(false, "Time stop: exit stale trade", group="V37 Upgrades", tooltip="If a position is open this many bars without hitting TP1, close it.")
int    time_stop_bars = input.int(20, "Time stop: max bars open", group="V37 Upgrades", minval=3)
msz_loose      = input.bool(true, "Loosen Massive Zones (more triggers)", group="Zones")

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// CORE CALCULATIONS
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
atr14    = ta.atr(14)
atr_fast = ta.atr(7)
atr_slow = ta.atr(28)
[diplus, diminus, adxV] = ta.dmi(14, 14)
atr_pct  = close > 0 ? atr14 / close * 100.0 : 0.0
c_body   = math.abs(close - open)
c_lwick  = math.min(open, close) - low
c_uwick  = high - math.max(open, close)
tf_sec   = timeframe.in_seconds(timeframe.period)

// === PER-TF AUTO: resolve combo + stop cap for the chart timeframe ===
// V44 2.5: cur_preset removed (dead — see preset-system removal above).
// V43: entry triggers reduced to VWAP + EMA. zone / retest / sweep removed (forced off). cons left dormant.
bool trig_zone_en  = false
bool trig_brk_en   = false
bool trig_sweep_en = false
bool trig_cons_en  = trig_cons_m
bool trig_vwap_en  = trig_vwap_m
bool trig_ema_en   = trig_ema_m
float cur_stopcap = tf_sec<=300 ? stopcap_5m : tf_sec<=900 ? stopcap_15m : tf_sec<=1800 ? stopcap_30m : tf_sec<=3600 ? stopcap_1h : stopcap_4h

// ============================ HTF SIGNAL (lightweight, no-repaint) ============================
bool   htf_sig_on = input.bool(true, "HTF signal: show + alert", group="HTF Signal", tooltip="Marks when the higher timeframe flips bull/bear (EMA20/50 alignment) as a confirmation overlay. No-repaint: confirmed HTF bars only. Fires alerts.")
string htf_mode   = input.string("Auto (next TF up)", "HTF source", options=["Auto (next TF up)", "Manual"], group="HTF Signal")
string sig_htf_manual = input.timeframe("60", "HTF (manual)", group="HTF Signal", tooltip="Used when HTF source = Manual.")
string sig_htf_tf     = htf_mode == "Manual" ? sig_htf_manual : (tf_sec<=300 ? "15" : tf_sec<=900 ? "60" : tf_sec<=1800 ? "60" : tf_sec<=3600 ? "240" : tf_sec<=14400 ? "D" : "W")
[sig_htf_c, sig_htf_e20, sig_htf_e50] = request.security(syminfo.tickerid, sig_htf_tf, [close[1], ta.ema(close,20)[1], ta.ema(close,50)[1]], lookahead=barmerge.lookahead_on)
bool   sig_htf_bull = not na(sig_htf_c) and not na(sig_htf_e20) and not na(sig_htf_e50) and sig_htf_c > sig_htf_e20 and sig_htf_e20 > sig_htf_e50
bool   sig_htf_bear = not na(sig_htf_c) and not na(sig_htf_e20) and not na(sig_htf_e50) and sig_htf_c < sig_htf_e20 and sig_htf_e20 < sig_htf_e50
bool   htf_long_evt  = htf_sig_on and sig_htf_bull and not sig_htf_bull[1]
bool   htf_short_evt = htf_sig_on and sig_htf_bear and not sig_htf_bear[1]
string htf_state = sig_htf_bull ? sig_htf_tf+" bull" : sig_htf_bear ? sig_htf_tf+" bear" : sig_htf_tf+" --"

float vol_ratio     = atr_fast > 0 and atr_slow > 0 ? atr_fast / atr_slow : 1.0
int   struct_lb_adp = math.max(5, math.min(math.round(14.0 / math.max(vol_ratio, 0.5)), 30))
int   struct_lb     = struct_adaptive ? struct_lb_adp : struct_lb_fix
float bar_range     = high - low
float bar_range_avg = ta.sma(bar_range, 20)

// F1: momentum veto + master EMA trend filter
float momo_atr_units = atr14 > 0 ? (close - close[5]) / atr14 : 0.0
bool momo_long_ok  = not momo_en or momo_atr_units >  momo_thresh
bool momo_short_ok = not momo_en or momo_atr_units < -momo_thresh
float trnd_f = ta.ema(close, trend_ema_f_in)
float trnd_s = ta.ema(close, trend_ema_s_in)
bool trend_up   = close > trnd_s and trnd_f > trnd_s
bool trend_down = close < trnd_s and trnd_f < trnd_s

plot(trend_show ? trnd_s : na, "Trend EMA50", color=trend_up ? color.new(color.lime,40) : trend_down ? color.new(color.red,40) : color.new(color.gray,60), linewidth=2)

// Auto cooldown
int cd_bars_auto = tf_sec <= 60    ? 3  :
                   tf_sec <= 300   ? 3  :
                   tf_sec <= 900   ? 5  :
                   tf_sec <= 1800  ? 8  :
                   tf_sec <= 3600  ? 15 :
                   tf_sec <= 14400 ? 8  : 3
int cd_bars = cd_auto ? cd_bars_auto : cd_bars_manual

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// SESSIONS
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
string sess_string = sess_filter == "RTH Only"    ? "0930-1600" :
                     sess_filter == "HS Windows"  ? "0930-1000,1030-1130,1330-1530" :
                     sess_filter == "Morning"     ? "0930-1130" :
                     sess_filter == "Afternoon"   ? "1330-1500" :
                     sess_filter == "Late Day"    ? "1500-1545" :
                     sess_filter == "Power Hour"  ? "1500-1600" :
                     sess_filter == "Futures All" ? "0830-1100,1330-1600,1900-2200,0200-0500" :
                     sess_filter == "Futures NY"  ? "0830-1600" : custom_sess

bool in_sess_bar = not sess_on or not na(time(timeframe.period, sess_string, sess_tz))
int  o_nh  = na(timenow) ? hour(time, sess_tz)   : hour(timenow, sess_tz)
int  o_nm  = na(timenow) ? minute(time, sess_tz) : minute(timenow, sess_tz)
int  o_now = o_nh * 60 + o_nm

bool in_lunch   = avoid_lunch   and o_now >= 11*60+30 and o_now < 13*60+30
bool in_open15  = avoid_open15  and o_now >= 9*60+30  and o_now < 9*60+45
bool in_close15 = avoid_close15 and o_now >= 15*60+45 and o_now < 16*60

string current_window =
     o_now >= 9*60+30  and o_now < 9*60+45  ? "Opening" :
     o_now >= 9*60+45  and o_now < 11*60+30 ? "Morning"   :
     o_now >= 11*60+30 and o_now < 13*60+30 ? "Lunch"  :
     o_now >= 13*60+30 and o_now < 15*60    ? "Afternoon" :
     o_now >= 15*60    and o_now < 15*60+45 ? "Power Hour":
     o_now >= 15*60+45 and o_now < 16*60    ? "MOC"    :
     o_now >= 4*60     and o_now < 9*60+30  ? "Pre-Mkt"  :
     o_now >= 16*60    and o_now < 20*60    ? "After-Hr"  : "Closed"

bool sess_active = sess_anytime ? true : (sess_on ? (in_sess_bar and not in_lunch and not in_open15 and not in_close15) : true)
bool blackout    = earnings_blackout or event_blackout
bool new_day     = dayofmonth != dayofmonth[1]

// F4: robust volume MA
float vol_ma = ta.sma(volume, 20)

// F5: PDH/PDL bundled into one security call (pdc removed)
pdhl_b() => [high[1], low[1]]
[pdh, pdl] = request.security(syminfo.tickerid, "D", pdhl_b(), lookahead=barmerge.lookahead_off)

var line pdh_line = na
var line pdl_line = na
if barstate.islastconfirmedhistory and show_pdh_pdl
    line.delete(pdh_line)
    line.delete(pdl_line)
    if not na(pdh)
        pdh_line := line.new(bar_index - 30, pdh, bar_index + 40, pdh, color=color.new(#FFD700, 30), style=line.style_dashed, width=1)
    if not na(pdl)
        pdl_line := line.new(bar_index - 30, pdl, bar_index + 40, pdl, color=color.new(#FFD700, 30), style=line.style_dashed, width=1)

var bool pdh_labeled = false
var bool pdl_labeled = false
if new_day
    pdh_labeled := false
    pdl_labeled := false
if not pdh_labeled and not na(pdh) and show_pdh_pdl and barstate.isconfirmed
    label.new(bar_index, pdh, "PDH " + str.tostring(pdh, "#.##"), style=label.style_label_left, color=color.new(#FFD700,50), textcolor=color.black, size=size.tiny)
    pdh_labeled := true
if not pdl_labeled and not na(pdl) and show_pdh_pdl and barstate.isconfirmed
    label.new(bar_index, pdl, "PDL " + str.tostring(pdl, "#.##"), style=label.style_label_left, color=color.new(#FFD700,50), textcolor=color.black, size=size.tiny)
    pdl_labeled := true

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// OPENING RANGE (9:30–10:00)
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
bool in_or_window = o_now >= 9*60+30 and o_now < 10*60
var float or_high = float(na)
var float or_low  = float(na)
var bool  or_set  = false
var box   or_box  = na

if new_day
    or_high := float(na)
    or_low  := float(na)
    or_set  := false
if in_or_window and in_sess_bar
    or_high := na(or_high) ? high : math.max(or_high, high)
    or_low  := na(or_low)  ? low  : math.min(or_low,  low)
if not in_or_window and not na(or_high) and not or_set
    or_set := true
    if show_or
        box.delete(or_box)
        or_box := box.new(bar_index - 12, or_high, bar_index + 50, or_low, bgcolor=color.new(#FFD700, 88), border_color=color.new(#FFD700, 40), border_width=1, text="OR", text_color=color.new(#FFD700,0), text_size=size.tiny)
if or_set and not na(or_box) and show_or
    box.set_right(or_box, bar_index + 10)

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// BUYER / SELLER VOLUME MODULE
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
float hl_range      = high - low
float vol_bull_raw  = hl_range > 0 ? volume * math.max(close - low,  0) / hl_range : volume * 0.5
float vol_bear_raw  = hl_range > 0 ? volume * math.max(high - close, 0) / hl_range : volume * 0.5
float vol_delta     = vol_bull_raw - vol_bear_raw
float vol_bull_ma   = ta.sma(vol_bull_raw, 20)
float vol_bear_ma   = ta.sma(vol_bear_raw, 20)

bool vol_bull_climax  = vol_bull_raw >= vol_bull_ma * vol_climax_mult and close > open and c_uwick < c_body * 0.4
bool vol_bear_climax  = vol_bear_raw >= vol_bear_ma * vol_climax_mult and close < open and c_lwick < c_body * 0.4
bool vol_bull_exhaust = vol_bull_raw >= vol_bull_ma * vol_climax_mult and c_uwick >= c_body * 0.5
bool vol_bear_exhaust = vol_bear_raw >= vol_bear_ma * vol_climax_mult and c_lwick >= c_body * 0.5
bool vol_bull_absorb  = vol_bull_raw >= vol_bull_ma * vol_absorb_mult and close > open and not vol_bull_climax
bool vol_bear_absorb  = vol_bear_raw >= vol_bear_ma * vol_absorb_mult and close < open and not vol_bear_climax
bool buyer_dominated  = vol_bull_raw > vol_bear_raw * 1.3
bool seller_dominated = vol_bear_raw > vol_bull_raw * 1.3
bool high_bull_vol    = vol_bull_absorb or vol_bull_climax
bool high_bear_vol    = vol_bear_absorb or vol_bear_climax
bool vol_confirm      = volume >= vol_ma * vc_mult

// ── DIRECTIONAL VOLUME CONFIRMATION (buyer/seller vs trend) ──
// trend + agreeing volume = confirm ; trend + opposing volume = WAIT (observe)
bool voldir_buyers     = buyer_dominated
bool voldir_sellers    = seller_dominated
bool voldir_conf_long  = voldir_buyers
bool voldir_conf_short = voldir_sellers
bool voldir_opp_long   = voldir_sellers
bool voldir_opp_short  = voldir_buyers
bool voldir_ok_long    = voldir_mode == "Off" ? true : voldir_mode == "Veto opposing" ? not voldir_opp_long  : voldir_conf_long
bool voldir_ok_short   = voldir_mode == "Off" ? true : voldir_mode == "Veto opposing" ? not voldir_opp_short : voldir_conf_short
// top grade needs strong AND direction-led volume (long wants buyers, short wants sellers)
bool vc_long  = vol_confirm and voldir_buyers
bool vc_short = vol_confirm and voldir_sellers

var float ph_vol_last = float(na)
var float ph_vol_prev = float(na)
var float pl_vol_last = float(na)
var float pl_vol_prev = float(na)

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// MACRO REGIME
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
string macro_trend_sym = not macro_auto_ref ? macro_spy_sym :
                         asset_macro_class == "METAL"    ? macro_gld_sym :
                         asset_macro_class == "ENERGY"   ? macro_uso_sym :
                         asset_macro_class == "CURRENCY" ? macro_dxy_sym : macro_spy_sym
string macro_vol_sym   = not macro_auto_ref ? macro_vix_sym :
                         asset_macro_class == "ENERGY"   ? macro_ovx_sym : macro_vix_sym

spy_b2() =>
    float c   = close
    float e20 = ta.ema(close, 20)
    float e50 = ta.ema(close, 50)
    [_dp2, _dm2, sadx] = ta.dmi(14, 14)
    [c, e20, e50, sadx]

vix_bundle() =>
    [close, ta.sma(close, 5), close[5]]

[macro_spy_close, macro_spy_e20, macro_spy_e50, macro_spy_adx] = request.security(macro_trend_sym, "D", spy_b2(), lookahead=barmerge.lookahead_off, ignore_invalid_symbol=true)
[macro_vix_raw, macro_vix, macro_vix_prev] = request.security(macro_vol_sym, "D", vix_bundle(), lookahead=barmerge.lookahead_off, ignore_invalid_symbol=true)

float macro_vix_change_pct = not na(macro_vix_prev) and macro_vix_prev > 0 ? (macro_vix - macro_vix_prev) / macro_vix_prev * 100.0 : 0.0

bool spy_uptrend   = not na(macro_spy_close) and macro_spy_close > macro_spy_e20 and macro_spy_e20 > macro_spy_e50
bool spy_downtrend = not na(macro_spy_close) and macro_spy_close < macro_spy_e20 and macro_spy_e20 < macro_spy_e50
bool spy_trending  = (spy_uptrend or spy_downtrend) and not na(macro_spy_adx) and macro_spy_adx >= macro_spy_adx_min
// V44 2.2: hard macro stand-down — no longs in a confirmed SPY downtrend, no shorts in a confirmed uptrend.
bool macro_long_ok  = not macro_en or not macro_standdown or not spy_downtrend
bool macro_short_ok = not macro_en or not macro_standdown or not spy_uptrend

string regime_raw = "—"
if not na(macro_vix)
    if macro_vix >= macro_vix_extreme
        regime_raw := "D"
    else if macro_vix >= macro_vix_volatile or macro_vix_change_pct >= 30.0
        regime_raw := "C"
    else if macro_vix < macro_vix_calm and spy_trending
        regime_raw := "A"
    else if macro_vix < macro_vix_volatile and not spy_trending
        regime_raw := "B"
    else if spy_trending
        regime_raw := "A"
    else
        regime_raw := "B"

var int    regime_persist_count = 0
var string regime_pending       = "—"
var string regime_confirmed     = "—"

int persist_needed = regime_raw == "D" ? 0 :
                     regime_confirmed == "C" and regime_raw == "A" ? macro_persist_n * 2 :
                     macro_persist_n

if regime_raw == "D"
    regime_confirmed     := "D"
    regime_pending       := "D"
    regime_persist_count := persist_needed
else if regime_raw == regime_pending
    regime_persist_count += 1
    if regime_persist_count >= persist_needed
        regime_confirmed := regime_raw
else
    regime_pending       := regime_raw
    regime_persist_count := 1

string macro_regime_auto = regime_confirmed != "—" ? regime_confirmed : regime_raw
string macro_regime      = macro_override ? macro_override_to : macro_regime_auto

bool macro_allow_trades = true
if macro_en
    if macro_regime == "D" and macro_block_d
        macro_allow_trades := false
    if macro_regime == "B" and macro_block_b_rng
        macro_allow_trades := false

bool macro_only_a_plus = macro_en and macro_regime == "C" and macro_only_a_in_c

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// MODULE 1 — STRUCTURE
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
ph = ta.pivothigh(high, struct_lb, struct_lb)
pl = ta.pivotlow( low,  struct_lb, struct_lb)

var float st_ph_last = float(na)
var float st_ph_prev = float(na)
var float st_pl_last = float(na)
var float st_pl_prev = float(na)

if not na(ph)
    bool sig_h = na(st_ph_last) or math.abs(ph - st_ph_last) / st_ph_last * 100.0 >= struct_tol_pct
    if sig_h
        st_ph_prev    := st_ph_last
        st_ph_last    := ph
        ph_vol_prev   := ph_vol_last
        ph_vol_last   := vol_bull_raw[struct_lb]
if not na(pl)
    bool sig_l = na(st_pl_last) or math.abs(pl - st_pl_last) / st_pl_last * 100.0 >= struct_tol_pct
    if sig_l
        st_pl_prev    := st_pl_last
        st_pl_last    := pl
        pl_vol_prev   := pl_vol_last
        pl_vol_last   := vol_bear_raw[struct_lb]

bool is_hh = not na(st_ph_last) and not na(st_ph_prev) and st_ph_last > st_ph_prev
bool is_lh = not na(st_ph_last) and not na(st_ph_prev) and st_ph_last < st_ph_prev
bool is_hl = not na(st_pl_last) and not na(st_pl_prev) and st_pl_last > st_pl_prev
bool is_ll = not na(st_pl_last) and not na(st_pl_prev) and st_pl_last < st_pl_prev

float div_thresh = 1.0 - vol_div_pct / 100.0
bool bull_div = div_en and not na(ph_vol_last) and not na(ph_vol_prev) and ph_vol_prev > 0 and is_hh and ph_vol_last < ph_vol_prev * div_thresh
bool bear_div = div_en and not na(pl_vol_last) and not na(pl_vol_prev) and pl_vol_prev > 0 and is_ll and pl_vol_last < pl_vol_prev * div_thresh

if bull_div and barstate.isconfirmed
    label.new(bar_index - struct_lb, st_ph_last + atr14*0.5, "BULL DIV\nVol DN", style=label.style_label_down, color=color.new(#FF8C00,20), textcolor=color.white, size=size.tiny)
if bear_div and barstate.isconfirmed
    label.new(bar_index - struct_lb, st_pl_last - atr14*0.5, "BEAR DIV\nVol DN", style=label.style_label_up, color=color.new(#FF8C00,20), textcolor=color.white, size=size.tiny)

// --- multi-degree structure (opt-in): a slower swing degree for trend context ---
ph2 = ta.pivothigh(high, mdeg_lb, mdeg_lb)
pl2 = ta.pivotlow( low,  mdeg_lb, mdeg_lb)
var float st2_ph_last = float(na)
var float st2_ph_prev = float(na)
var float st2_pl_last = float(na)
var float st2_pl_prev = float(na)
if not na(ph2)
    st2_ph_prev := st2_ph_last
    st2_ph_last := ph2
if not na(pl2)
    st2_pl_prev := st2_pl_last
    st2_pl_last := pl2
int st2_state = (not na(st2_ph_prev) and not na(st2_pl_prev)) ? (st2_ph_last > st2_ph_prev and st2_pl_last > st2_pl_prev ? 1 : st2_ph_last < st2_ph_prev and st2_pl_last < st2_pl_prev ? 2 : 3) : 3
var int st_state      = 0
var int st_state_prev = 0
st_state_prev := st_state
if is_hh and is_hl
    st_state := 1
else if is_ll and is_lh
    st_state := 2
else if (is_hh and is_ll) or (is_hl and is_lh)
    st_state := 3

bool st_bos_bull = st_state == 1 and not na(st_ph_last) and high > st_ph_last and high[1] <= st_ph_last
bool st_bos_bear = st_state == 2 and not na(st_pl_last) and low  < st_pl_last and low[1]  >= st_pl_last

bool st_choch_bull = false
bool st_choch_bear = false
if st_state_prev == 2 and not na(st_ph_last) and close > st_ph_last and close[1] <= st_ph_last
    st_choch_bull := true
    st_state      := 0
if st_state_prev == 1 and not na(st_pl_last) and close < st_pl_last and close[1] >= st_pl_last
    st_choch_bear := true
    st_state      := 0

var int choch_bull_bar = -9999
var int choch_bear_bar = -9999
if st_choch_bull
    choch_bull_bar := bar_index
if st_choch_bear
    choch_bear_bar := bar_index
bool choch_bull_active = (bar_index - choch_bull_bar) <= 5
bool choch_bear_active = (bar_index - choch_bear_bar) <= 5

// F1: live close-confirmed breaks
bool live_bos_down = not na(st_pl_last) and close < st_pl_last and close[1] >= st_pl_last
bool live_bos_up   = not na(st_ph_last) and close > st_ph_last and close[1] <= st_ph_last
var int live_down_bar = -9999
var int live_up_bar   = -9999
if live_bos_down or st_choch_bear
    live_down_bar := bar_index
if live_bos_up or st_choch_bull
    live_up_bar := bar_index
bool down_break_active = livebreak_en and (bar_index - live_down_bar) <= 8
bool up_break_active   = livebreak_en and (bar_index - live_up_bar)   <= 8

// F1: final structure gates — state/choch/live-break, AND momentum, AND master trend
// ACCURACY layer: symmetric raw setup existence (momentum only; bias handled by floor)
bool struct_long_ok  = (st_state == 1 or choch_bull_active or up_break_active)   and momo_long_ok
bool struct_short_ok = (st_state == 2 or choch_bear_active or down_break_active) and momo_short_ok

if struct_show and not na(ph)
    string lbl_h = is_hh ? "HH" : is_lh ? "LH" : "PH"
    color  clr_h = is_hh ? color.lime : is_lh ? color.red : color.gray
    label.new(bar_index - struct_lb, ph + atr14*0.3, lbl_h, style=label.style_label_down, color=clr_h, textcolor=color.white, size=size.tiny)
if struct_show and not na(pl)
    string lbl_l = is_hl ? "HL" : is_ll ? "LL" : "PL"
    color  clr_l = is_hl ? color.lime : is_ll ? color.red : color.gray
    label.new(bar_index - struct_lb, pl - atr14*0.3, lbl_l, style=label.style_label_up, color=clr_l, textcolor=color.white, size=size.tiny)
if struct_show_bos and st_bos_bull and barstate.isconfirmed
    label.new(bar_index, low - atr14*0.8, "BOS UP", style=label.style_label_up, color=color.new(color.lime,10), textcolor=color.black, size=size.small)
if struct_show_bos and st_bos_bear and barstate.isconfirmed
    label.new(bar_index, high + atr14*0.8, "BOS DN", style=label.style_label_down, color=color.new(color.red,10), textcolor=color.white, size=size.small)
if struct_show_bos and st_choch_bull and barstate.isconfirmed
    label.new(bar_index, low - atr14*0.6, "CHoCH UP", style=label.style_label_up, color=color.new(color.aqua,10), textcolor=color.black, size=size.small)
if struct_show_bos and st_choch_bear and barstate.isconfirmed
    label.new(bar_index, high + atr14*0.6, "CHoCH DN", style=label.style_label_down, color=color.new(color.orange,10), textcolor=color.black, size=size.small)

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// MODULE 2 — LOCAL REGIME
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
int local_regime = atr_pct >= local_atr_hi ? 3 : adxV >= local_adx_min ? 1 : 2
bool local_trend    = local_regime == 1
bool local_range    = local_regime == 2
bool local_volatile = local_regime == 3
bool local_regime_gate = (not local_block_rng or not local_range) and (not local_block_vol or not local_volatile)

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// MODULE 3 — SWEEP DETECTION
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
float roll_hi = ta.highest(high[1], struct_lb)
float roll_lo = ta.lowest( low[1],  struct_lb)
float swing_hi_lvl = not na(st_ph_last) ? st_ph_last : roll_hi
float swing_lo_lvl = not na(st_pl_last) ? st_pl_last : roll_lo
var float sweep_atr_stored = float(na)
float sweep_min = atr14 * sweep_depth_atr

bool sell_side_sweep = sweep_en and low  < swing_lo_lvl - sweep_min and close > swing_lo_lvl
bool buy_side_sweep  = sweep_en and high > swing_hi_lvl + sweep_min and close < swing_hi_lvl

bool bull_sweep_with   = sell_side_sweep and struct_long_ok
bool bull_sweep_contra = sell_side_sweep and not struct_long_ok
bool bear_sweep_with   = buy_side_sweep  and struct_short_ok
bool bear_sweep_contra = buy_side_sweep  and not struct_short_ok

var int bull_sweep_b = -9999
var int bear_sweep_b = -9999
var float bull_sweep_lo = float(na)
var float bear_sweep_hi = float(na)

if bull_sweep_with
    bull_sweep_b      := bar_index
    bull_sweep_lo     := low
    sweep_atr_stored  := atr14
if bear_sweep_with
    bear_sweep_b      := bar_index
    bear_sweep_hi     := high
    sweep_atr_stored  := atr14

int sweep_window = math.min(struct_lb, 8)
bool bull_sweep_active = (bar_index - bull_sweep_b) <= sweep_window
bool bear_sweep_active = (bar_index - bear_sweep_b) <= sweep_window

bool pdl_sweep = sell_side_sweep and not na(pdl) and math.abs(swing_lo_lvl - pdl) <= atr14 * 1.0
bool pdh_sweep = buy_side_sweep  and not na(pdh) and math.abs(swing_hi_lvl - pdh) <= atr14 * 1.0

var line swept_lo_line = na
var line swept_hi_line = na

if bull_sweep_with
    line.delete(swept_lo_line)
    if sweep_show_level
        swept_lo_line := line.new(bar_index - struct_lb, swing_lo_lvl, bar_index + 30, swing_lo_lvl, color=color.new(color.lime,40), style=line.style_dashed, width=1)
    string ssl_lbl = pdl_sweep ? "SELL-SIDE SWEEP (PDL)\nStops Taken - BUY" : "SELL-SIDE SWEEP\nStops Taken - BUY"
    label.new(bar_index, low - atr14*0.5, ssl_lbl, style=label.style_label_up, color=color.new(#00E676, pdl_sweep ? 5 : 15), textcolor=color.white, size=size.tiny)
if bear_sweep_with
    line.delete(swept_hi_line)
    if sweep_show_level
        swept_hi_line := line.new(bar_index - struct_lb, swing_hi_lvl, bar_index + 30, swing_hi_lvl, color=color.new(color.red,40), style=line.style_dashed, width=1)
    string bsl_lbl = pdh_sweep ? "BUY-SIDE SWEEP (PDH)\nStops Taken - SELL" : "BUY-SIDE SWEEP\nStops Taken - SELL"
    label.new(bar_index, high + atr14*0.5, bsl_lbl, style=label.style_label_down, color=color.new(#FF1744, pdh_sweep ? 5 : 15), textcolor=color.white, size=size.tiny)
if sweep_show_contra and bull_sweep_contra and barstate.isconfirmed
    label.new(bar_index, low - atr14*0.4, "Sell-Side?", style=label.style_label_up, color=color.new(color.gray,50), textcolor=color.silver, size=size.tiny)
if sweep_show_contra and bear_sweep_contra and barstate.isconfirmed
    label.new(bar_index, high + atr14*0.4, "Buy-Side?", style=label.style_label_down, color=color.new(color.gray,50), textcolor=color.silver, size=size.tiny)

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// MODULE 4 — HTF BIAS  (F3: no close[1] double-lag)
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
string htf_auto = tf_sec <= 60    ? "15"  :
                  tf_sec <= 300   ? "60"  :
                  tf_sec <= 900   ? "240" :
                  tf_sec <= 3600  ? "D"   :
                  tf_sec <= 14400 ? "W"   : "M"
string htf_used = htf_dynamic ? htf_auto : htf_manual

htf_bundle() =>
    [ta.ema(close, htf_ema_fast), ta.ema(close, htf_ema_slow), close]

[htf_e1, htf_e2, htf_c] = request.security(syminfo.tickerid, htf_used, htf_bundle(), lookahead=barmerge.lookahead_off)
bool htf_bull = htf_en and not na(htf_c) and htf_c > htf_e1 and htf_e1 > htf_e2
bool htf_bear = htf_en and not na(htf_c) and htf_c < htf_e1 and htf_e1 < htf_e2

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// UNIFIED DIRECTIONAL BIAS SPINE  (THE FIX — symmetric, single source)
// dir_bias is one signed number; LONG and SHORT read the SAME value.
//   HTF stack ±2  |  EMA21/50 stack ±2 (gated by trendfilter_en)  |  DMI ±1
// |dir_bias| >= 2 = directional; else NONE (chop).
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
bool dmi_bull = not na(diplus) and not na(diminus) and diplus > diminus and adxV >= local_adx_min
bool dmi_bear = not na(diplus) and not na(diminus) and diminus > diplus and adxV >= local_adx_min
int  dir_bias = (htf_bull ? w_htf : htf_bear ? -w_htf : 0) + (trendfilter_en ? (trend_up ? w_trend : trend_down ? -w_trend : 0) : 0) + (dmi_bull ? w_dmi : dmi_bear ? -w_dmi : 0)
// bias N-bar confirm: only flip when the raw read persists (anti-whipsaw); 1 = instant
string mb_raw = dir_bias >= bias_thresh ? "LONG" : dir_bias <= -bias_thresh ? "SHORT" : "NONE"
var string master_bias = "NONE"
var string mb_pending = "NONE"
var int mb_count = 0
if mb_raw == mb_pending
    mb_count += 1
else
    mb_pending := mb_raw
    mb_count := 1
if mb_count >= bias_confirm_bars
    master_bias := mb_raw
bool with_long  = master_bias == "LONG"
bool with_short = master_bias == "SHORT"

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// MULTI-TF DEMAND / SUPPLY ZONES  (security floats; draw stacked higher TFs + always 4h)
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
int chart_min = math.max(1, tf_sec / 60)
mtf_ob() =>
    var float dt = float(na)
    var float db = float(na)
    var float stp = float(na)
    var float sbt = float(na)
    float aa = ta.atr(14)
    bool up_ob = close > high[1] and close[1] < open[1] and math.abs(close-open) >= aa*mtf_body_min
    bool dn_ob = close < low[1]  and close[1] > open[1] and math.abs(close-open) >= aa*mtf_body_min
    if up_ob
        dt := open[1]
        db := low[1]
    if dn_ob
        stp := high[1]
        sbt := open[1]
    if not na(db) and close < db
        dt := float(na)
        db := float(na)
    if not na(stp) and close > stp
        stp := float(na)
        sbt := float(na)
    [dt, db, stp, sbt]
[d5t,d5b,s5t,s5b]         = request.security(syminfo.tickerid, "5",   mtf_ob(), lookahead=barmerge.lookahead_off)
[d15t,d15b,s15t,s15b]     = request.security(syminfo.tickerid, "15",  mtf_ob(), lookahead=barmerge.lookahead_off)
[d30t,d30b,s30t,s30b]     = request.security(syminfo.tickerid, "30",  mtf_ob(), lookahead=barmerge.lookahead_off)
[d60t,d60b,s60t,s60b]     = request.security(syminfo.tickerid, "60",  mtf_ob(), lookahead=barmerge.lookahead_off)
[d240t,d240b,s240t,s240b] = request.security(syminfo.tickerid, "240", mtf_ob(), lookahead=barmerge.lookahead_off)

bool show5_z   = mtf_show and 5   > chart_min
bool show15_z  = mtf_show and 15  > chart_min
bool show30_z  = mtf_show and 30  > chart_min
bool show60_z  = mtf_show and 60  > chart_min
bool show240_z = mtf_show

var box[] mtf_boxes = array.new_box()
f_zone(show_it, t, b, is_dem, lbl, transp) =>
    if show_it and not na(t) and not na(b)
        color cc = is_dem ? color.green : color.red
        array.push(mtf_boxes, box.new(bar_index - 2, t, bar_index + 18, b, bgcolor=color.new(cc, transp), border_color=color.new(cc, math.max(0, transp-30)), border_width=1, text=lbl, text_color=color.new(cc, 0), text_size=size.tiny, text_halign=text.align_left))
if barstate.islastconfirmedhistory and mtf_show
    if array.size(mtf_boxes) > 0
        for i = 0 to array.size(mtf_boxes) - 1
            box.delete(array.get(mtf_boxes, i))
        array.clear(mtf_boxes)
    f_zone(show5_z,   d5t,   d5b,   true,  "5m D",   86)
    f_zone(show5_z,   s5t,   s5b,   false, "5m S",   86)
    f_zone(show15_z,  d15t,  d15b,  true,  "15m D",  82)
    f_zone(show15_z,  s15t,  s15b,  false, "15m S",  82)
    f_zone(show30_z,  d30t,  d30b,  true,  "30m D",  76)
    f_zone(show30_z,  s30t,  s30b,  false, "30m S",  76)
    f_zone(show60_z,  d60t,  d60b,  true,  "1h D",   68)
    f_zone(show60_z,  s60t,  s60b,  false, "1h S",   68)
    f_zone(show240_z, d240t, d240b, true,  "4h D",   58)
    f_zone(show240_z, s240t, s240b, false, "4h S",   58)

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// MODULE 5 — ORDER BLOCKS
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
var box[] bull_obs = array.new_box()
var box[] bear_obs = array.new_box()
var bool  in_bull_ob  = false
var bool  in_bear_ob  = false
var float bull_ob_top = 0.0
var float bull_ob_bot = 0.0
var float bear_ob_top = 0.0
var float bear_ob_bot = 0.0

int  ob_bw        = high_bull_vol or high_bear_vol ? 2 : 1
bool ob_strong    = c_body >= atr14 * ob_body_min and volume >= vol_ma * 0.7
bool bull_ob_form = close > high[1] and close[1] < open[1] and ob_strong
bool bear_ob_form = close < low[1]  and close[1] > open[1] and ob_strong

if bull_ob_form
    if array.size(bull_obs) >= ob_max
        box.delete(array.get(bull_obs, 0))
        array.remove(bull_obs, 0)
    array.push(bull_obs, box.new(bar_index[1], open[1], bar_index+1, low[1], bgcolor=show_zones ? color.new(color.green,86) : color.new(color.green,100), border_color=show_zones ? color.new(color.green,40) : color.new(color.green,100), border_width=ob_bw))
if bear_ob_form
    if array.size(bear_obs) >= ob_max
        box.delete(array.get(bear_obs, 0))
        array.remove(bear_obs, 0)
    array.push(bear_obs, box.new(bar_index[1], high[1], bar_index+1, open[1], bgcolor=show_zones ? color.new(color.red,86) : color.new(color.red,100), border_color=show_zones ? color.new(color.red,40) : color.new(color.red,100), border_width=ob_bw))

if array.size(bull_obs) > 0
    for i = array.size(bull_obs) - 1 to 0
        ob = array.get(bull_obs, i)
        box.set_right(ob, bar_index+1)
        if close < box.get_bottom(ob) or math.abs(close - box.get_top(ob)) > atr14*zone_stale_atr
            box.delete(ob)
            array.remove(bull_obs, i)
if array.size(bear_obs) > 0
    for i = array.size(bear_obs) - 1 to 0
        ob = array.get(bear_obs, i)
        box.set_right(ob, bar_index+1)
        if close > box.get_top(ob) or math.abs(close - box.get_bottom(ob)) > atr14*zone_stale_atr
            box.delete(ob)
            array.remove(bear_obs, i)

in_bull_ob  := false
in_bear_ob  := false
bull_ob_top := 0.0
bull_ob_bot := 0.0
bear_ob_top := 0.0
bear_ob_bot := 0.0

if array.size(bull_obs) > 0
    for i = 0 to array.size(bull_obs) - 1
        ob = array.get(bull_obs, i)
        if low <= box.get_top(ob) and high >= box.get_bottom(ob)
            in_bull_ob  := true
            bull_ob_top := box.get_top(ob)
            bull_ob_bot := box.get_bottom(ob)
if array.size(bear_obs) > 0
    for i = 0 to array.size(bear_obs) - 1
        ob = array.get(bear_obs, i)
        if low <= box.get_top(ob) and high >= box.get_bottom(ob)
            in_bear_ob  := true
            bear_ob_top := box.get_top(ob)
            bear_ob_bot := box.get_bottom(ob)

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// MODULE 6 — FVG
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
var box[] bull_fvgs  = array.new_box()
var box[] bear_fvgs  = array.new_box()
var bool  in_bull_fvg = false
var bool  in_bear_fvg = false

if low > high[2]
    if array.size(bull_fvgs) >= fvg_max
        box.delete(array.get(bull_fvgs, 0))
        array.remove(bull_fvgs, 0)
    array.push(bull_fvgs, box.new(bar_index[2], low, bar_index+1, high[2], bgcolor=show_zones ? color.new(color.blue,90) : color.new(color.blue,100), border_color=show_zones ? color.new(color.blue,60) : color.new(color.blue,100), border_width=1))
if high < low[2]
    if array.size(bear_fvgs) >= fvg_max
        box.delete(array.get(bear_fvgs, 0))
        array.remove(bear_fvgs, 0)
    array.push(bear_fvgs, box.new(bar_index[2], low[2], bar_index+1, high, bgcolor=show_zones ? color.new(color.orange,90) : color.new(color.orange,100), border_color=show_zones ? color.new(color.orange,60) : color.new(color.orange,100), border_width=1))

if array.size(bull_fvgs) > 0
    for i = array.size(bull_fvgs) - 1 to 0
        f = array.get(bull_fvgs, i)
        box.set_right(f, bar_index+1)
        if close < box.get_bottom(f)
            box.delete(f)
            array.remove(bull_fvgs, i)
if array.size(bear_fvgs) > 0
    for i = array.size(bear_fvgs) - 1 to 0
        f = array.get(bear_fvgs, i)
        box.set_right(f, bar_index+1)
        if close > box.get_top(f)
            box.delete(f)
            array.remove(bear_fvgs, i)

in_bull_fvg := false
in_bear_fvg := false
if array.size(bull_fvgs) > 0
    for i = 0 to array.size(bull_fvgs) - 1
        f = array.get(bull_fvgs, i)
        if low <= box.get_top(f) and high >= box.get_bottom(f)
            in_bull_fvg := true
if array.size(bear_fvgs) > 0
    for i = 0 to array.size(bear_fvgs) - 1
        f = array.get(bear_fvgs, i)
        if low <= box.get_top(f) and high >= box.get_bottom(f)
            in_bear_fvg := true

bool at_bull_zone = in_bull_ob or in_bull_fvg
bool at_bear_zone = in_bear_ob or in_bear_fvg

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// MODULE 7 — PATTERNS
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
float c1_body = math.abs(close[1] - open[1])
float c2_body = math.abs(close[2] - open[2])
float ms_mid  = (open[2] + close[2]) / 2.0

bool morning_star = pat_en and close[2] < open[2] and c2_body >= atr14*0.8 and c1_body <= atr14*0.4 and close > open and c_body >= atr14*0.6 and close >= ms_mid
bool evening_star = pat_en and close[2] > open[2] and c2_body >= atr14*0.8 and c1_body <= atr14*0.4 and close < open and c_body >= atr14*0.6 and close <= ms_mid

var int ms_bar = -999
var int es_bar = -999
if morning_star
    ms_bar := bar_index
if evening_star
    es_bar := bar_index
bool ms_active = (bar_index - ms_bar) <= 4
bool es_active = (bar_index - es_bar) <= 4

if pat_show and morning_star and barstate.isconfirmed
    label.new(bar_index, low - atr14*1.0, "Morning Star", style=label.style_label_up, color=color.new(color.lime,10), textcolor=color.white, size=size.small)
if pat_show and evening_star and barstate.isconfirmed
    label.new(bar_index, high + atr14*1.0, "Evening Star", style=label.style_label_down, color=color.new(color.red,10), textcolor=color.white, size=size.small)

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// MASSIVE BUY / SELL ZONE
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
var bool sweep_in_bull_zone = false
var bool sweep_in_bear_zone = false

if bull_sweep_with
    sweep_in_bull_zone := at_bull_zone
if bear_sweep_with
    sweep_in_bear_zone := at_bear_zone
if not bull_sweep_active
    sweep_in_bull_zone := false
if not bear_sweep_active
    sweep_in_bear_zone := false

bool msz_buy_trigger  = msz_en and bull_sweep_active and close > open and c_body >= atr14 * (msz_loose?0.6:1.0) and (high_bull_vol or msz_loose) and sweep_in_bull_zone
bool msz_sell_trigger = msz_en and bear_sweep_active and close < open and c_body >= atr14 * (msz_loose?0.6:1.0) and (high_bear_vol or msz_loose) and sweep_in_bear_zone

var box[] buy_zone_boxes  = array.new_box()
var box[] sell_zone_boxes = array.new_box()

if msz_buy_trigger
    if array.size(buy_zone_boxes) >= msz_max
        box.delete(array.get(buy_zone_boxes, 0))
        array.remove(buy_zone_boxes, 0)
    array.push(buy_zone_boxes, box.new(bar_index, math.max(open,close), bar_index+1, math.min(open,close), bgcolor=color.new(#00E676,75), border_color=color.new(#00E676,20), border_width=2, text="DEMAND ZONE", text_color=color.white, text_size=size.small))
if msz_sell_trigger
    if array.size(sell_zone_boxes) >= msz_max
        box.delete(array.get(sell_zone_boxes, 0))
        array.remove(sell_zone_boxes, 0)
    array.push(sell_zone_boxes, box.new(bar_index, math.max(open,close), bar_index+1, math.min(open,close), bgcolor=color.new(#FF1744,75), border_color=color.new(#FF1744,20), border_width=2, text="SUPPLY ZONE", text_color=color.white, text_size=size.small))

bool in_msz_buy  = false
bool in_msz_sell = false

if array.size(buy_zone_boxes) > 0
    for i = array.size(buy_zone_boxes) - 1 to 0
        b = array.get(buy_zone_boxes, i)
        box.set_right(b, bar_index+1)
        bool piz_b = low <= box.get_top(b) and high >= box.get_bottom(b)
        if close < box.get_bottom(b) - atr14*zone_stale_atr
            box.delete(b)
            array.remove(buy_zone_boxes, i)
        else
            box.set_bgcolor(b, color.new(#00E676, piz_b ? 50 : 75))
            if piz_b
                in_msz_buy := true
if array.size(sell_zone_boxes) > 0
    for i = array.size(sell_zone_boxes) - 1 to 0
        b = array.get(sell_zone_boxes, i)
        box.set_right(b, bar_index+1)
        bool piz_s = low <= box.get_top(b) and high >= box.get_bottom(b)
        if close > box.get_top(b) + atr14*zone_stale_atr
            box.delete(b)
            array.remove(sell_zone_boxes, i)
        else
            box.set_bgcolor(b, color.new(#FF1744, piz_s ? 50 : 75))
            if piz_s
                in_msz_sell := true

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// COOLDOWN  (new sweep same direction bypasses)
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
var int last_long_bar  = int(na)
var int last_short_bar = int(na)
bool cd_long_bypass  = bull_sweep_with
bool cd_short_bypass = bear_sweep_with
bool cd_long  = cd_long_bypass  or na(last_long_bar)  or (bar_index - last_long_bar)  > cd_bars
bool cd_short = cd_short_bypass or na(last_short_bar) or (bar_index - last_short_bar) > cd_bars

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// SCORING  (symmetric align on master_bias | divergence penalty | trend-aware floor)
// Max = 12 points
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
int macro_bonus_L = (macro_regime == "A" and spy_uptrend)   ? 1 : 0
int macro_bonus_S = (macro_regime == "A" and spy_downtrend) ? 1 : 0

int score_struct_L  = struct_long_ok  ? 2 : 0
int score_struct_S  = struct_short_ok ? 2 : 0
int score_align_L   = master_bias == "LONG"  ? 2 : master_bias == "NONE" ? 1 : 0
int score_align_S   = master_bias == "SHORT" ? 2 : master_bias == "NONE" ? 1 : 0
int score_zone_L    = at_bull_zone ? (in_bull_ob ? 2 : 1) : 0
int score_zone_S    = at_bear_zone ? (in_bear_ob ? 2 : 1) : 0
// V36: score_htf removed (HTF already counted via dir_bias -> master_bias -> score_align)
int score_sweep_L   = bull_sweep_active ? 2 : 0
int score_sweep_S   = bear_sweep_active ? 2 : 0
int score_pattern_L = ms_active ? 1 : 0
int score_pattern_S = es_active ? 1 : 0
int div_penalty_L   = bull_div ? -1 : 0
int div_penalty_S   = bear_div ? -1 : 0

// score zeroed if struct gate fails (structure-mandatory)
int long_score  = struct_long_ok  ? (score_struct_L + score_align_L + score_zone_L + score_sweep_L + score_pattern_L + macro_bonus_L + div_penalty_L) : 0
int short_score = struct_short_ok ? (score_struct_S + score_align_S + score_zone_S + score_sweep_S + score_pattern_S + macro_bonus_S + div_penalty_S) : 0

// Trend-aware floor: with-bias B (floor_with) | counter-bias A (floor_counter) | NONE->counter
// TREND-AWARE FLOOR: with-bias fires at floor_with (B); counter-bias needs floor_counter (A); NONE uses counter.
int long_floor  = with_long  ? floor_with : floor_counter
int short_floor = with_short ? floor_with : floor_counter
string lf_raw = (struct_long_ok  and long_score  >= long_floor)  ? (long_score  >= 9 ? "A+" : long_score  >= 7 ? "A" : "B") : ""
string sf_raw = (struct_short_ok and short_score >= short_floor) ? (short_score >= 9 ? "A+" : short_score >= 7 ? "A" : "B") : ""
// ACCURACY-layer setup presence (objective, independent of timing gates)
bool acc_long_setup  = lf_raw != ""
bool acc_short_setup = sf_raw != ""
string lf = lf_raw
string sf = sf_raw

if vc_en and not vc_long
    if lf == "A+"
        lf := "A"
    else if lf == "A"
        lf := "B"
if vc_en and not vc_short
    if sf == "A+"
        sf := "A"
    else if sf == "A"
        sf := "B"

if macro_only_a_plus
    if lf != "A+"
        lf := ""
    if sf != "A+"
        sf := ""

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// ENTRY / SL / TP / SIZING
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
float sl_buf_eff = sl_buf_atr * ticker_sl_mult
float sl_cap     = atr14 * (per_tf_stop ? cur_stopcap : sl_max_atr)

// ── ENTRY TRIGGER SUPPORT (VWAP / EMA20-50 / consolidation range) ──
float vwap_sess = ta.vwap(hlc3)
float vwap_wk   = ta.vwap(hlc3, timeframe.change("W"))
float vwap_mo   = ta.vwap(hlc3, timeframe.change("M"))
float vwap_v  = vwap_anchor=="Weekly" ? vwap_wk : vwap_anchor=="Monthly" ? vwap_mo : vwap_sess
float ema20   = ta.ema(close, 20)
float ema50   = ta.ema(close, 50)
float ema9    = ta.ema(close, 9)
float cons_hi = ta.highest(high, cons_len)
float cons_lo = ta.lowest(low,  cons_len)
bool  is_cons = (cons_hi - cons_lo) < atr14 * cons_mult

// ── ZONE-ANCHORED ENTRY (fixed/latched, no drifting close) ──
// nearest valid zone whose ENTRY EDGE is AT price (genuine retest) -> keeps entry near price so TP/SL lead it
float at_thr = atr14 * entry_near_atr
float dz_top = float(na)
float dz_bot = float(na)
if mtf_show and not na(d240t) and math.abs(close - d240t) <= at_thr
    dz_top := d240t
    dz_bot := d240b
else if mtf_show and not na(d60t) and math.abs(close - d60t) <= at_thr
    dz_top := d60t
    dz_bot := d60b
else if mtf_show and not na(d30t) and math.abs(close - d30t) <= at_thr
    dz_top := d30t
    dz_bot := d30b
else if mtf_show and not na(d15t) and math.abs(close - d15t) <= at_thr
    dz_top := d15t
    dz_bot := d15b
else if bull_ob_top > 0 and math.abs(close - bull_ob_top) <= at_thr
    dz_top := bull_ob_top
    dz_bot := bull_ob_bot
else if in_bull_fvg
    dz_top := close
    dz_bot := close - atr14
float sz_bot = float(na)
float sz_top = float(na)
if mtf_show and not na(s240b) and math.abs(close - s240b) <= at_thr
    sz_bot := s240b
    sz_top := s240t
else if mtf_show and not na(s60b) and math.abs(close - s60b) <= at_thr
    sz_bot := s60b
    sz_top := s60t
else if mtf_show and not na(s30b) and math.abs(close - s30b) <= at_thr
    sz_bot := s30b
    sz_top := s30t
else if mtf_show and not na(s15b) and math.abs(close - s15b) <= at_thr
    sz_bot := s15b
    sz_top := s15t
else if bear_ob_top > 0 and math.abs(close - bear_ob_top) <= at_thr
    sz_bot := bear_ob_bot
    sz_top := bear_ob_top
else if in_bear_fvg
    sz_bot := close
    sz_top := close + atr14

// entry: zone retest if AT a zone; else breakout-retest of the broken pivot (price just past it); else market (frozen at latch)
bool brk_retest_long  = up_break_active   and not na(st_ph_last) and close >= st_ph_last and (close - st_ph_last) <= atr14 * 2.0
bool brk_retest_short = down_break_active  and not na(st_pl_last) and close <= st_pl_last and (st_pl_last - close) <= atr14 * 2.0
float le_raw = not na(dz_top) ? dz_top : brk_retest_long  ? st_ph_last : close
float se_raw = not na(sz_bot) ? sz_bot : brk_retest_short ? st_pl_last : close
// V44 2.3: trigger-relative stop — anchor to the nearest active VWAP/EMA the entry reclaims
f_near(float c, bool below) =>
    float best = float(na)
    arr = array.from(vwap_sess, use_vwap2 ? vwap_wk : float(na), ema9, ema20, use_ema3 ? ema50 : float(na))
    for v in arr
        if not na(v) and (below ? v <= c : v >= c) and (na(best) or (below ? v > best : v < best))
            best := v
    best
float trig_supp_l = f_near(close, true)    // nearest VWAP/EMA <= price (long stop anchor)
float trig_res_s  = f_near(close, false)   // nearest VWAP/EMA >= price (short stop anchor)
float lsl_anchor = stop_anchor == "Trigger-relative" and not na(trig_supp_l) ? trig_supp_l - atr14*sl_buf_eff : (not na(dz_bot) ? dz_bot - atr14*sl_buf_eff : (not na(bull_sweep_lo) and bull_sweep_active ? bull_sweep_lo - atr14*sl_buf_eff : (not na(st_pl_last) ? st_pl_last - atr14*sl_buf_eff : le_raw - atr14*1.5)))
float ssl_anchor = stop_anchor == "Trigger-relative" and not na(trig_res_s) ? trig_res_s + atr14*sl_buf_eff : (not na(sz_top) ? sz_top + atr14*sl_buf_eff : (not na(bear_sweep_hi) and bear_sweep_active ? bear_sweep_hi + atr14*sl_buf_eff : (not na(st_ph_last) ? st_ph_last + atr14*sl_buf_eff : se_raw + atr14*1.5)))

// LATCH: freeze entry+SL on setup rising edge; hold while setup persists; live otherwise
var float le  = float(na)
var float se  = float(na)
var float lsl = float(na)
var float ssl = float(na)
var bool  long_armed  = false
var bool  short_armed = false
var float zone_le = float(na)
var float zone_se = float(na)
if acc_long_setup and not long_armed
    le  := le_raw
    lsl := math.max(le_raw - sl_cap, math.min(lsl_anchor, le_raw - atr14*min_stop_atr))
    zone_le := not na(dz_top) ? dz_top : float(na)
    long_armed := true
if not acc_long_setup
    long_armed := false
if acc_short_setup and not short_armed
    se  := se_raw
    ssl := math.min(se_raw + sl_cap, math.max(ssl_anchor, se_raw + atr14*min_stop_atr))
    zone_se := not na(sz_bot) ? sz_bot : float(na)
    short_armed := true
if not acc_short_setup
    short_armed := false
if not long_armed
    le  := le_raw
    lsl := math.max(le_raw - sl_cap, math.min(lsl_anchor, le_raw - atr14*min_stop_atr))
if not short_armed
    se  := se_raw
    ssl := math.min(se_raw + sl_cap, math.max(ssl_anchor, se_raw + atr14*min_stop_atr))
float lrk = le - lsl
float srk = ssl - se
float lt1 = le + lrk * tp1_rr
float lt2 = le + lrk * tp2_rr
float st1 = se - srk * tp1_rr
float st2 = se - srk * tp2_rr
float lrr = lrk > 0 ? (lt2 - le) / lrk : 0.0
float srr = srk > 0 ? (se - st2) / srk  : 0.0

float lrr_from_close = lrk > 0 and close > lsl ? (lt2 - close) / (close - lsl) : 0.0
float srr_from_close = srk > 0 and close < ssl ? (close - st2) / (ssl - close)  : 0.0

// ── TP/SL VALIDITY GUARD (degenerate-geometry block — the tp/sl fix) ──
// require correct ordering AND a real minimum risk; broken geometry never fires/draws/feeds CB
bool geo_long  = not na(le) and not na(lsl) and not na(lt2) and le > lsl and lt1 > le and lt2 > lt1 and (le - lsl) >= atr14 * 0.2
bool geo_short = not na(se) and not na(ssl) and not na(st2) and se < ssl and st1 < se and st2 < st1 and (ssl - se) >= atr14 * 0.2

int l_btp2 = math.max(1, math.min(bar_range_avg > 0 ? math.round((lt2-le)/bar_range_avg) : 0, 100))
int s_btp2 = math.max(1, math.min(bar_range_avg > 0 ? math.round((se-st2)/bar_range_avg) : 0, 100))

f_btt(bars) =>
    float tm = float(bars) * float(tf_sec) / 60.0
    tm < 60.0 ? str.tostring(math.round(tm)) + "m" : tm < 1440.0 ? str.tostring(math.floor(tm / 60.0)) + "h" : str.tostring(math.floor(tm / 1440.0)) + "d"

string l_hold_str = f_btt(l_btp2)
string s_hold_str = f_btt(s_btp2)

float l_risk_dlr = 0.0
float s_risk_dlr = 0.0
float l_rwd_dlr  = 0.0
float s_rwd_dlr  = 0.0
float l_pos      = 0.0
float s_pos      = 0.0
int   l_units    = 0
int   s_units    = 0

if asset_class == "FUTURE"
    int lbr = lrk > 0 ? math.floor(eff_risk_dlr / (lrk * ticker_pt_val)) : 0
    int sbr = srk > 0 ? math.floor(eff_risk_dlr / (srk * ticker_pt_val)) : 0
    l_units    := lbr
    s_units    := sbr
    l_risk_dlr := lrk * ticker_pt_val * l_units
    s_risk_dlr := srk * ticker_pt_val * s_units
    l_rwd_dlr  := (lt2 - le) * ticker_pt_val * l_units
    s_rwd_dlr  := (se - st2) * ticker_pt_val * s_units
    l_pos      := l_risk_dlr
    s_pos      := s_risk_dlr
else
    int lbr2 = lrk > 0  ? math.floor(max_risk_dlr / lrk)   : 0
    int lbs  = close > 0 ? math.floor(max_pos_dlr  / close) : 0
    int sbr2 = srk > 0  ? math.floor(max_risk_dlr / srk)    : 0
    int sbs  = close > 0 ? math.floor(max_pos_dlr  / close) : 0
    l_units    := math.max(1, math.min(lbr2, lbs))
    s_units    := math.max(1, math.min(sbr2, sbs))
    l_risk_dlr := lrk * l_units
    s_risk_dlr := srk * s_units
    l_rwd_dlr  := (lt2 - le) * l_units
    s_rwd_dlr  := (se - st2) * s_units
    l_pos      := close * l_units
    s_pos      := close * s_units

bool gate_units_L = (asset_class == "FUTURE" and strat_fixed_qty == 0) ? l_units > 0 : true
bool gate_units_S = (asset_class == "FUTURE" and strat_fixed_qty == 0) ? s_units > 0 : true

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// CIRCUIT BREAKER — real SL/TP crossing  (F2: decrement open_positions here)
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
var int   cb_consec_losses  = 0
var float cb_daily_pnl      = 0.0
var int   cb_last_signal    = 0
var float cb_entry_price    = 0.0
var int   cb_entry_bar      = -9999
var float cb_sl_stored      = float(na)
var float cb_tp1_stored     = float(na)
var int   cb_units_stored   = 0
var int   open_positions    = 0

if new_day
    cb_consec_losses := 0
    cb_daily_pnl     := 0.0
    open_positions   := 0

if cb_last_signal != 0 and bar_index > cb_entry_bar and not na(cb_sl_stored)
    bool cb_stopped  = cb_last_signal == 1 ? low  <= cb_sl_stored  : high >= cb_sl_stored
    bool cb_won      = cb_last_signal == 1 ? high >= cb_tp1_stored : low  <= cb_tp1_stored
    bool cb_timeout  = (bar_index - cb_entry_bar) >= 5
    float pts_risk   = math.abs(cb_entry_price - cb_sl_stored)
    float pts_reward = math.abs(cb_tp1_stored  - cb_entry_price)
    float dlr_factor = asset_class == "FUTURE" ? ticker_pt_val * float(cb_units_stored) : float(cb_units_stored)

    if cb_stopped
        cb_consec_losses += 1
        cb_daily_pnl     -= pts_risk * dlr_factor
        cb_last_signal   := 0
        open_positions   := math.max(0, open_positions - 1)   // F2
    else if cb_won
        cb_consec_losses := 0
        cb_daily_pnl     += pts_reward * dlr_factor
        cb_last_signal   := 0
        open_positions   := math.max(0, open_positions - 1)   // F2
    else if cb_timeout
        cb_last_signal   := 0
        open_positions   := math.max(0, open_positions - 1)   // F2

bool cb_blocked   = cb_en and (cb_consec_losses >= cb_max_losses or cb_daily_pnl <= -cb_daily_dlr)
bool gate_max_pos = open_positions < max_open_pos

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// SIGNAL FIRE
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// V44 2.5: orphaned reaction-at-level layer removed (react_long/short + tag/rj_wick/reclaim/engulf
//  helpers were computed but NEVER consumed; firing uses the VWAP/EMA trigger). entry_mode still
//  gates whether a trigger is required (need_react) and the one-shot lockout (need_lock).
bool need_react     = entry_mode != "Momentum"
bool need_lock      = entry_mode == "Surgical"
bool trig_vwap_long  = trig_vwap_en  and ((low  <= vwap_sess and close > vwap_sess) or (use_vwap2 and low  <= vwap_wk and close > vwap_wk)) and close > open
bool trig_vwap_short = trig_vwap_en  and ((high >= vwap_sess and close < vwap_sess) or (use_vwap2 and high >= vwap_wk and close < vwap_wk)) and close < open
bool trig_ema_long   = trig_ema_en   and ((low  <= ema9 and close > ema9) or (low  <= ema20 and close > ema20) or (use_ema3 and low  <= ema50 and close > ema50)) and close > open
bool trig_ema_short  = trig_ema_en   and ((high >= ema9 and close < ema9) or (high >= ema20 and close < ema20) or (use_ema3 and high >= ema50 and close < ema50)) and close < open
bool trig_cons_long  = trig_cons_en  and is_cons[1] and close > cons_hi[1] and close > open and (not cons_vol_filt or volume > vol_ma)
bool trig_cons_short = trig_cons_en  and is_cons[1] and close < cons_lo[1] and close < open and (not cons_vol_filt or volume > vol_ma)
float zlow_n  = ta.lowest(low,  mitig_lb)
float zhigh_n = ta.highest(high, mitig_lb)
bool bull_zone_fresh = na(dz_bot) or zlow_n  >= dz_bot
bool bear_zone_fresh = na(sz_top) or zhigh_n <= sz_top
bool rvol_ok = not rvol_gate or (vol_ma > 0 and volume / vol_ma >= rvol_min)
// V44 2.4: confluence instead of OR-of-5 (validate, don't mine)
int  n_trig_long  = (trig_vwap_long?1:0)  + (trig_ema_long?1:0)  + (trig_cons_long?1:0)
int  n_trig_short = (trig_vwap_short?1:0) + (trig_ema_short?1:0) + (trig_cons_short?1:0)
bool conf_long  = trig_confluence=="Any (OR)" ? n_trig_long>=1  : trig_confluence==">=2 triggers" ? n_trig_long>=2  : (trig_vwap_long  and trig_ema_long)
bool conf_short = trig_confluence=="Any (OR)" ? n_trig_short>=1 : trig_confluence==">=2 triggers" ? n_trig_short>=2 : (trig_vwap_short and trig_ema_short)
bool trigger_long    = conf_long  and rvol_ok
bool trigger_short   = conf_short and rvol_ok
float trig_sl_mult_l = not pertrig_stops ? 1.0 : ((trig_vwap_long  or trig_ema_long)  ? sl_mult_wide : 1.0)
float trig_sl_mult_s = not pertrig_stops ? 1.0 : ((trig_vwap_short or trig_ema_short) ? sl_mult_wide : 1.0)
bool react_ok_long  = not need_react or trigger_long
bool react_ok_short = not need_react or trigger_short
var float lock_long_ref  = float(na)
var float lock_short_ref = float(na)
bool long_unlocked  = not need_lock or na(lock_long_ref)  or st_pl_last != lock_long_ref
bool short_unlocked = not need_lock or na(lock_short_ref) or st_ph_last != lock_short_ref

// --- entry gates: HTF filter, trigger quality, multi-degree (all opt-in) ---
int  trig_quality_l = (vol_confirm?1:0) + (at_bull_zone?1:0) + (st_state==1?1:0) + (sig_htf_bull?1:0) + ((vol_ma>0 and volume/vol_ma>=1.2)?1:0)
int  trig_quality_s = (vol_confirm?1:0) + (at_bear_zone?1:0) + (st_state==2?1:0) + (sig_htf_bear?1:0) + ((vol_ma>0 and volume/vol_ma>=1.2)?1:0)
bool trigq_ok_l = not trigq_gate or trig_quality_l >= trigq_min
bool trigq_ok_s = not trigq_gate or trig_quality_s >= trigq_min
bool htf_gate_ok_l = not htf_gate_on or (htf_gate_mode=="Require aligned" ? sig_htf_bull : not sig_htf_bear)
bool htf_gate_ok_s = not htf_gate_on or (htf_gate_mode=="Require aligned" ? sig_htf_bear : not sig_htf_bull)
bool mdeg_ok_l = not mdeg_gate or st2_state != 2
bool mdeg_ok_s = not mdeg_gate or st2_state != 1
bool long_fire  = long_signals_on  and lf != "" and sess_active and cd_long  and
                  struct_long_ok   and local_regime_gate and macro_allow_trades and macro_long_ok and
                  lrr >= min_rr and close > lsl and geo_long and voldir_ok_long and react_ok_long and long_unlocked and gate_units_L and gate_max_pos and
                  not cb_blocked  and not blackout and htf_gate_ok_l and trigq_ok_l and mdeg_ok_l
bool short_fire = short_signals_on and sf != "" and sess_active and cd_short and
                  struct_short_ok  and local_regime_gate and macro_allow_trades and macro_short_ok and
                  srr >= min_rr and close < ssl and geo_short and voldir_ok_short and react_ok_short and short_unlocked and gate_units_S and gate_max_pos and
                  not cb_blocked  and not blackout and htf_gate_ok_s and trigq_ok_s and mdeg_ok_s

if long_fire
    last_long_bar    := bar_index
    open_positions   += 1
    cb_last_signal   := 1
    cb_entry_price   := le
    cb_entry_bar     := bar_index
    cb_sl_stored     := lsl
    cb_tp1_stored    := lt1
    cb_units_stored  := l_units
    lock_long_ref    := st_pl_last
if short_fire
    last_short_bar   := bar_index
    open_positions   += 1
    cb_last_signal   := -1
    cb_entry_price   := se
    cb_entry_bar     := bar_index
    cb_sl_stored     := ssl
    cb_tp1_stored    := st1
    cb_units_stored  := s_units
    lock_short_ref   := st_ph_last

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// STRATEGY EXECUTION  (drives the TradingView Strategy Tester)
//  Entry = limit at the latched zone/level (toggle: market). Scale: 50% at TP1,
//  then move the remaining stop to breakeven, runner to TP2. Levels FROZEN at signal.
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
var float trade_sl  = float(na)
var float trade_tp1 = float(na)
var float trade_tp2 = float(na)
var float trade_ep  = float(na)
var int   entry_bar = na
var bool  tp1_filled = false
var float trail_l   = float(na)
var float trail_s   = float(na)
bool flat = strategy.position_size == 0

// --- L18 eval guardrails: daily loss breaker + trailing-DD halt (equity-based, incl. open) ---
var float day_start_eq = float(na)
bool new_day_eq = ta.change(time("D")) != 0
if new_day_eq or na(day_start_eq)
    day_start_eq := strategy.equity
float day_pl = strategy.equity - day_start_eq
bool day_breaker = eval_on and day_pl <= -daily_loss_limit
var float peak_eq = float(na)
peak_eq := na(peak_eq) ? strategy.equity : math.max(peak_eq, strategy.equity)
float trail_floor = peak_eq - trail_dd
bool trail_halt = eval_on and strategy.equity <= trail_floor + trail_buffer
bool eval_block = day_breaker or trail_halt

int qtyL = strat_fixed_qty > 0 ? strat_fixed_qty : (eval_on ? math.max(eval_min_contracts, l_units) : math.max(1, l_units))
int qtyS = strat_fixed_qty > 0 ? strat_fixed_qty : (eval_on ? math.max(eval_min_contracts, s_units) : math.max(1, s_units))

if long_fire and flat and not eval_block
    if entry_market
        strategy.entry("L", strategy.long, qty=qtyL, comment=lf)
    else
        strategy.entry("L", strategy.long, qty=qtyL, limit=le, comment=lf)
    trade_sl  := pertrig_stops ? le - (le - lsl) * trig_sl_mult_l : lsl
    trade_tp1 := lt1
    trade_tp2 := lt2
    trade_ep  := le
    trail_l   := float(na)
    entry_bar := bar_index
    tp1_filled := false
if short_fire and flat and not eval_block
    if entry_market
        strategy.entry("S", strategy.short, qty=qtyS, comment=sf)
    else
        strategy.entry("S", strategy.short, qty=qtyS, limit=se, comment=sf)
    trade_sl  := pertrig_stops ? se + (ssl - se) * trig_sl_mult_s : ssl
    trade_tp1 := st1
    trade_tp2 := st2
    trade_ep  := se
    trail_s   := float(na)
    entry_bar := bar_index
    tp1_filled := false

// cancel a resting entry if its setup disappears before it fills
if flat and not acc_long_setup
    strategy.cancel("L")
if flat and not acc_short_setup
    strategy.cancel("S")

// manage open LONG: TP1 partial, then configurable runner stop + target
if strategy.position_size > 0
    if not tp1_filled and high >= trade_tp1
        tp1_filled := true
    if time_stop_on and not tp1_filled and (bar_index - entry_bar) >= time_stop_bars
        strategy.close("L", comment="time stop")
    if exit_on_choch and st_choch_bear
        strategy.close("L", comment="CHoCH exit")
    float stopL = trade_sl
    if tp1_filled
        if after_tp1 == "Trail (ATR)"
            trail_l := na(trail_l) ? close - atr14*trail_atr : math.max(trail_l, close - atr14*trail_atr)
            stopL := trail_l
        else if after_tp1 == "Trail (structure)"
            float cand_l = not na(st_pl_last) ? st_pl_last - atr14*sl_buf_eff : trade_ep
            trail_l := na(trail_l) ? cand_l : math.max(trail_l, cand_l)
            stopL := trail_l
        else if after_tp1 == "BE + lock"
            stopL := trade_ep + (trade_ep - trade_sl) * be_lock_rr
        else if after_tp1 == "Keep original SL"
            stopL := trade_sl
        else
            stopL := trade_ep
    float tgtL = runner_target == "Fixed TP2" ? trade_tp2 : float(na)
    strategy.exit("Lx1", from_entry="L", qty_percent=tp1_pct, stop=trade_sl, limit=trade_tp1)
    strategy.exit("Lx2", from_entry="L", stop=stopL, limit=tgtL)
// manage open SHORT
if strategy.position_size < 0
    if not tp1_filled and low <= trade_tp1
        tp1_filled := true
    if time_stop_on and not tp1_filled and (bar_index - entry_bar) >= time_stop_bars
        strategy.close("S", comment="time stop")
    if exit_on_choch and st_choch_bull
        strategy.close("S", comment="CHoCH exit")
    float stopS = trade_sl
    if tp1_filled
        if after_tp1 == "Trail (ATR)"
            trail_s := na(trail_s) ? close + atr14*trail_atr : math.min(trail_s, close + atr14*trail_atr)
            stopS := trail_s
        else if after_tp1 == "Trail (structure)"
            float cand_s = not na(st_ph_last) ? st_ph_last + atr14*sl_buf_eff : trade_ep
            trail_s := na(trail_s) ? cand_s : math.min(trail_s, cand_s)
            stopS := trail_s
        else if after_tp1 == "BE + lock"
            stopS := trade_ep - (trade_sl - trade_ep) * be_lock_rr
        else if after_tp1 == "Keep original SL"
            stopS := trade_sl
        else
            stopS := trade_ep
    float tgtS = runner_target == "Fixed TP2" ? trade_tp2 : float(na)
    strategy.exit("Sx1", from_entry="S", qty_percent=tp1_pct, stop=trade_sl, limit=trade_tp1)
    strategy.exit("Sx2", from_entry="S", stop=stopS, limit=tgtS)

// V44 2.8: EOD-flat — force-close once per day at eod_hhmm (disciplined/windowed mode only)
int  eod_min    = math.floor(eod_hhmm / 100) * 60 + (eod_hhmm % 100)
bool eod_active = eod_flat and sess_on and not sess_anytime
var bool eod_done = false
if new_day
    eod_done := false
if eod_active and not eod_done and o_now >= eod_min
    if strategy.position_size != 0
        strategy.close_all(comment="EOD flat")
    eod_done := true

// V25 sign-test tripwires (silent if direction logic correct)

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// TP1 → BREAKEVEN NOTIFICATION
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
var bool  long_active   = false
var bool  short_active  = false
var float active_be_l   = float(na)
var float active_tp1_l  = float(na)
var float active_be_s   = float(na)
var float active_tp1_s  = float(na)
var bool  tp1_notified_l = false
var bool  tp1_notified_s = false

if long_fire
    long_active      := true
    short_active     := false
    active_be_l      := le
    active_tp1_l     := lt1
    tp1_notified_l   := false
if short_fire
    short_active     := true
    long_active      := false
    active_be_s      := se
    active_tp1_s     := st1
    tp1_notified_s   := false

if long_active and not tp1_notified_l and not na(active_tp1_l)
    if high >= active_tp1_l
        tp1_notified_l := true
        label.new(bar_index, high + atr14*0.6, "TP1 hit - Move SL to BE\n" + str.tostring(active_be_l, "#.##"), style=label.style_label_down, color=color.new(#FFD700, 15), textcolor=color.black, size=size.small)
        long_active := false
if short_active and not tp1_notified_s and not na(active_tp1_s)
    if low <= active_tp1_s
        tp1_notified_s := true
        label.new(bar_index, low - atr14*0.6, "TP1 hit - Move SL to BE\n" + str.tostring(active_be_s, "#.##"), style=label.style_label_up, color=color.new(#FFD700, 15), textcolor=color.black, size=size.small)
        short_active := false

if long_active  and not na(cb_sl_stored) and low  <= cb_sl_stored
    long_active  := false
if short_active and not na(cb_sl_stored) and high >= cb_sl_stored
    short_active := false

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// VOLUME-TYPED CANDLE COLORING
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
color vc_bar =
     long_fire  and lf == "A+" ? color.new(color.yellow, 0)  :
     long_fire  and lf == "A"  ? color.new(color.lime,   0)  :
     short_fire and sf == "A+" ? color.new(color.yellow, 0)  :
     short_fire and sf == "A"  ? color.new(color.red,    0)  :
     vol_bull_climax  ? color.new(#00FF41, 0)   :
     vol_bear_climax  ? color.new(#FF0000, 0)   :
     vol_bull_exhaust ? color.new(#FFD700, 10)  :
     vol_bear_exhaust ? color.new(#FF8C00, 10)  :
     vol_bull_absorb  ? color.new(#00BCD4, 20)  :
     vol_bear_absorb  ? color.new(#C62828, 20)  :
     buyer_dominated  ? color.new(color.teal,   35) :
     seller_dominated ? color.new(color.maroon, 35) : na
barcolor(vol_color_bars ? vc_bar : na, title="Volume-typed bar color")

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// VOLUME EVENT LABELS
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
if vol_show_labels and barstate.isconfirmed
    if vol_bull_climax
        label.new(bar_index, low - atr14*0.7, "BUY CLIMAX\n" + str.tostring(math.round(vol_bull_raw/1000)) + "K", style=label.style_label_up, color=color.new(#00E676,20), textcolor=color.white, size=size.tiny)
    if vol_bear_climax
        label.new(bar_index, high + atr14*0.7, "SELL CLIMAX\n" + str.tostring(math.round(vol_bear_raw/1000)) + "K", style=label.style_label_down, color=color.new(#FF1744,20), textcolor=color.white, size=size.tiny)
    if vol_bull_exhaust and not vol_bull_climax
        label.new(bar_index, high + atr14*0.4, "BUY EXHAUST", style=label.style_label_down, color=color.new(#FFD700,25), textcolor=color.black, size=size.tiny)
    if vol_bear_exhaust and not vol_bear_climax
        label.new(bar_index, low - atr14*0.4, "SELL EXHAUST", style=label.style_label_up, color=color.new(#FF8C00,25), textcolor=color.black, size=size.tiny)

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// SIGNAL LABELS + LINES
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
color lclr = lf == "A+" ? color.yellow : lf == "A" ? color.lime  : color.teal
color sclr = sf == "A+" ? color.yellow : sf == "A" ? color.red   : color.orange

plotshape(long_fire,  title="Long",  style=shape.labelup,   location=location.belowbar, color=lclr, text="L", textcolor=lf=="A+" ? color.black : color.white, size=size.small)
plotshape(short_fire, title="Short", style=shape.labeldown, location=location.abovebar, color=sclr, text="S", textcolor=sf=="A+" ? color.black : color.white, size=size.small)
plotshape(htf_long_evt,  title="HTF flip bull", style=shape.triangleup,   location=location.belowbar, color=color.new(color.teal,0),   size=size.tiny, text="HTF", textcolor=color.teal)
plotshape(htf_short_evt, title="HTF flip bear", style=shape.triangledown, location=location.abovebar, color=color.new(color.orange,0), size=size.tiny, text="HTF", textcolor=color.orange)
alertcondition(htf_long_evt,  title="HTF flip BULL", message="HIGHSTRIKE: higher timeframe flipped BULLISH")
alertcondition(htf_short_evt, title="HTF flip BEAR", message="HIGHSTRIKE: higher timeframe flipped BEARISH")
bool eqh = eqhl_on and not na(st_ph_last) and not na(st_ph_prev) and math.abs(st_ph_last - st_ph_prev)/st_ph_prev*100.0 <= eqhl_tol
bool eql = eqhl_on and not na(st_pl_last) and not na(st_pl_prev) and math.abs(st_pl_last - st_pl_prev)/st_pl_prev*100.0 <= eqhl_tol
plotshape(eqh and not eqh[1], title="Equal highs", style=shape.square, location=location.abovebar, color=color.new(color.fuchsia,30), size=size.tiny, text="EQH", textcolor=color.fuchsia)
plotshape(eql and not eql[1], title="Equal lows",  style=shape.square, location=location.belowbar, color=color.new(color.fuchsia,30), size=size.tiny, text="EQL", textcolor=color.fuchsia)

f_vctx(is_long) =>
    bool bc = is_long ? vol_bull_climax  : vol_bear_climax
    bool ba = is_long ? vol_bull_absorb  : vol_bear_absorb
    bool be = is_long ? vol_bull_exhaust : vol_bear_exhaust
    bool bd = is_long ? bull_div         : bear_div
    string vs = bc ? "CLIMAX" : ba ? "ABSORB" : be ? "EXHAUST" : "-"
    bd ? vs + " DIV" : vs

if long_fire
    string sl_type = bull_sweep_active and not na(bull_sweep_lo) ? "SL(sweep)" : "SL(struct)"
    string lt = lf + " LONG | " + str.tostring(long_score) + "/12 | Macro:" + macro_regime + "\nE "    + str.tostring(le,  "#.##") + " | " + sl_type + " " + str.tostring(lsl, "#.##") + "\nTP1 "  + str.tostring(lt1, "#.##") + " | TP2 " + str.tostring(lt2, "#.##") + "\nRR(E) "+ str.tostring(lrr, "#.##") + " RR(now) " + str.tostring(lrr_from_close,"#.##") + "\nHold ~"+ l_hold_str + " | Vol: " + f_vctx(true) + (in_msz_buy ? " | DEMAND" : "") + (pdl_sweep  ? " | PDL" : "")
    if show_dollars
        string uw = asset_class == "FUTURE" ? "x" : "sh"
        lt += "\nR$" + str.tostring(l_risk_dlr,"#") + " W$" + str.tostring(l_rwd_dlr,"#") + "\n" + str.tostring(l_units) + uw + " = $" + str.tostring(l_pos,"#")
    label.new(bar_index+1, le, lt, style=label.style_label_right, color=color.new(lclr,30), textcolor=color.white, size=size.tiny)

if short_fire
    string sl_type_s = bear_sweep_active and not na(bear_sweep_hi) ? "SL(sweep)" : "SL(struct)"
    string st_txt = sf + " SHORT | " + str.tostring(short_score) + "/12 | Macro:" + macro_regime + "\nE "    + str.tostring(se,  "#.##") + " | " + sl_type_s + " " + str.tostring(ssl, "#.##") + "\nTP1 "  + str.tostring(st1, "#.##") + " | TP2 " + str.tostring(st2, "#.##") + "\nRR(E) "+ str.tostring(srr, "#.##") + " RR(now) " + str.tostring(srr_from_close,"#.##") + "\nHold ~"+ s_hold_str + " | Vol: " + f_vctx(false) + (in_msz_sell ? " | SUPPLY" : "") + (pdh_sweep   ? " | PDH" : "")
    if show_dollars
        string uw = asset_class == "FUTURE" ? "x" : "sh"
        st_txt += "\nR$" + str.tostring(s_risk_dlr,"#") + " W$" + str.tostring(s_rwd_dlr,"#") + "\n" + str.tostring(s_units) + uw + " = $" + str.tostring(s_pos,"#")
    label.new(bar_index+1, se, st_txt, style=label.style_label_right, color=color.new(sclr,30), textcolor=color.white, size=size.tiny)

var line ln_le  = na
var line ln_lsl = na
var line ln_lt1 = na
var line ln_lt2 = na
var line ln_se  = na
var line ln_ssl = na
var line ln_st1 = na
var line ln_st2 = na

if long_fire and show_levels
    line.delete(ln_le)
    line.delete(ln_lsl)
    line.delete(ln_lt1)
    line.delete(ln_lt2)
    ln_le  := line.new(bar_index, le,  bar_index+30, le,  color=color.new(color.lime,10),  style=line.style_solid,  width=2)
    ln_lsl := line.new(bar_index, lsl, bar_index+30, lsl, color=color.new(color.red,20),   style=line.style_dashed, width=1)
    ln_lt1 := line.new(bar_index, lt1, bar_index+30, lt1, color=color.new(color.green,40), style=line.style_dotted, width=1)
    ln_lt2 := line.new(bar_index, lt2, bar_index+30, lt2, color=color.new(color.green,20), style=line.style_dashed, width=1)
if short_fire and show_levels
    line.delete(ln_se)
    line.delete(ln_ssl)
    line.delete(ln_st1)
    line.delete(ln_st2)
    ln_se  := line.new(bar_index, se,  bar_index+30, se,  color=color.new(color.red,10),   style=line.style_solid,  width=2)
    ln_ssl := line.new(bar_index, ssl, bar_index+30, ssl, color=color.new(color.red,20),   style=line.style_dashed, width=1)
    ln_st1 := line.new(bar_index, st1, bar_index+30, st1, color=color.new(color.green,40), style=line.style_dotted, width=1)
    ln_st2 := line.new(bar_index, st2, bar_index+30, st2, color=color.new(color.green,20), style=line.style_dashed, width=1)

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// BACKGROUND TINTS
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
color macro_bg = macro_regime == "A" ? color.new(color.green,  97) :
                 macro_regime == "B" ? color.new(color.gray,   97) :
                 macro_regime == "C" ? color.new(color.orange, 95) :
                 macro_regime == "D" ? color.new(color.red,    92) : na
bgcolor(show_macro_bg and macro_en ? macro_bg : na)
bgcolor(local_range    and local_block_rng ? color.new(color.gray,95)   : na)
bgcolor(local_volatile and local_block_vol ? color.new(color.maroon,95) : na)
bgcolor(in_lunch    ? color.new(color.gray,92)   : na)
bgcolor(in_open15   ? color.new(color.orange,93) : na)
bgcolor(in_close15  ? color.new(color.orange,93) : na)
bgcolor(sess_on and not in_sess_bar ? color.new(color.gray,94) : na)
bgcolor(blackout    ? color.new(color.red,90) : na)
bgcolor(cb_blocked  ? color.new(color.red,88) : na)
bgcolor(in_msz_buy  ? color.new(#00E676,93)   : na)
bgcolor(in_msz_sell ? color.new(#FF1744,93)   : na)

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// ALERTS
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// DASHBOARD  (28 rows)
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
var table tbl = table.new(position.top_right, 2, 15, bgcolor=color.new(color.black,72), border_color=color.new(color.gray,55), border_width=1, frame_color=color.new(color.gray,45), frame_width=1)

if barstate.islastconfirmedhistory and show_dashboard
    string rzn_l = not long_signals_on?"L off":not sess_active?"session":not cd_long?"cooldown":not local_regime_gate?"regime":not macro_allow_trades?("macro "+macro_regime):lrr<min_rr?"RR<min":close<=lsl?"stop":not geo_long?"geo":not voldir_ok_long?"vol":not react_ok_long?"no trig":not long_unlocked?"locked":not gate_units_L?"0 units":not gate_max_pos?"max pos":cb_blocked?"CB":blackout?"blackout":"ready"
    string rzn_s = not short_signals_on?"S off":not sess_active?"session":not cd_short?"cooldown":not local_regime_gate?"regime":not macro_allow_trades?("macro "+macro_regime):srr<min_rr?"RR<min":close>=ssl?"stop":not geo_short?"geo":not voldir_ok_short?"vol":not react_ok_short?"no trig":not short_unlocked?"locked":not gate_units_S?"0 units":not gate_max_pos?"max pos":cb_blocked?"CB":blackout?"blackout":"ready"
    string trg     = trigger_long ? (trig_vwap_long?"vwap":trig_ema_long?"ema":trig_cons_long?"cons":"—") : trigger_short ? (trig_vwap_short?"vwap":trig_ema_short?"ema":trig_cons_short?"cons":"—") : "—"
    string why_s   = long_fire?("L FIRED "+trg):short_fire?("S FIRED "+trg):acc_long_setup?("L: "+rzn_l):acc_short_setup?("S: "+rzn_s):"—"
    color  c_why   = (long_fire or short_fire)?color.lime:(acc_long_setup or acc_short_setup)?color.yellow:color.gray
    string d_bias  = master_bias + " (" + str.tostring(dir_bias) + ")"
    color  c_bias  = master_bias=="LONG"?color.lime:master_bias=="SHORT"?color.red:color.gray
    string d_setup = acc_long_setup?("LONG "+lf+(with_long?" w":" CTR")):acc_short_setup?("SHORT "+sf+(with_short?" w":" CTR")):"none"
    color  c_setup = acc_long_setup?(with_long?color.lime:color.orange):acc_short_setup?(with_short?color.red:color.orange):color.gray
    string d_reg   = macro_regime+" | "+(local_regime==1?"TREND":local_regime==2?"RNG":"VOL")+" | VIX "+str.tostring(macro_vix,"#.#")
    color  c_reg   = macro_regime=="A"?color.lime:macro_regime=="D"?color.red:color.yellow
    string d_str   = (st_state==1?"UP":st_state==2?"DN":st_state==3?"RNG":"form")+" | EMA "+(trend_up?"UP":trend_down?"DN":"flat")+" | ADX "+str.tostring(adxV,"#")
    string d_htf   = (htf_bull?"BULL":htf_bear?"BEAR":"neut")+" "+htf_used+" | Z:"+(in_msz_buy?"DEMAND":in_msz_sell?"SUPPLY":at_bull_zone?"demand":at_bear_zone?"supply":"—")
    string d_vol   = (vol_bull_climax?"BUY CLIMAX":vol_bear_climax?"SELL CLIMAX":vol_bull_absorb?"buy abs":vol_bear_absorb?"sell abs":"—")+" | "+(voldir_buyers?"BUYERS":voldir_sellers?"SELLERS":"bal")
    string d_swp   = bull_sweep_active?"SELL-SIDE (L)":bear_sweep_active?"BUY-SIDE (S)":"—"
    string d_ent   = long_armed?("L @ "+str.tostring(le,"#.##")+" RR "+str.tostring(lrr,"#.#")):short_armed?("S @ "+str.tostring(se,"#.##")+" RR "+str.tostring(srr,"#.#")):"—"
    string uw3     = asset_class=="FUTURE"?"x":"sh"
    string d_sz    = long_armed?(str.tostring(l_units)+uw3+" R$"+str.tostring(l_risk_dlr,"#")+" ~"+l_hold_str):short_armed?(str.tostring(s_units)+uw3+" R$"+str.tostring(s_risk_dlr,"#")+" ~"+s_hold_str):"—"
    string d_sess  = (sess_anytime?"24/7":sess_active?"ACTIVE":"closed")+" | pos "+str.tostring(open_positions)+"/"+str.tostring(max_open_pos)
    color  c_sess  = sess_active?color.lime:color.gray
    string d_cb    = cb_blocked?("TRIPPED $"+str.tostring(cb_daily_pnl,"#")):("OK "+str.tostring(cb_consec_losses)+"L $"+str.tostring(cb_daily_pnl,"#"))
    color  c_cb    = cb_blocked?color.red:color.lime
    string mode_s  = entry_mode=="Surgical"?"SURG":entry_mode=="Hybrid"?"HYB":"MOM"
    table.cell(tbl,0,0,"HIGHSTRIKE V44",  text_color=color.yellow, text_size=size.small, bgcolor=color.new(color.navy,20))
    table.cell(tbl,1,0,asset_class+" · "+mode_s+(per_tf_stop?(" · "+str.tostring(cur_stopcap,"#.#")+"R"):""), text_color=color.silver, text_size=size.tiny, bgcolor=color.new(color.navy,20))
    table.cell(tbl,0,1,"Bias",     text_color=color.white,  text_size=size.tiny, bgcolor=color.new(color.teal,55))
    table.cell(tbl,1,1,d_bias,     text_color=c_bias,       text_size=size.tiny, bgcolor=color.new(color.teal,55))
    table.cell(tbl,0,2,"Setup",    text_color=color.white,  text_size=size.tiny, bgcolor=color.new(color.teal,70))
    table.cell(tbl,1,2,d_setup,    text_color=c_setup,      text_size=size.tiny, bgcolor=color.new(color.teal,70))
    table.cell(tbl,0,3,"Why",      text_color=color.white,  text_size=size.tiny, bgcolor=color.new(color.teal,70))
    table.cell(tbl,1,3,why_s,      text_color=c_why,        text_size=size.tiny, bgcolor=color.new(color.teal,70))
    table.cell(tbl,0,4,"Regime",   text_color=color.silver, text_size=size.tiny)
    table.cell(tbl,1,4,d_reg,      text_color=c_reg,        text_size=size.tiny)
    table.cell(tbl,0,5,"Trend",    text_color=color.silver, text_size=size.tiny)
    table.cell(tbl,1,5,d_str,      text_color=color.aqua,   text_size=size.tiny)
    table.cell(tbl,0,6,"HTF/Zone", text_color=color.silver, text_size=size.tiny)
    table.cell(tbl,1,6,d_htf,      text_color=color.aqua,   text_size=size.tiny)
    table.cell(tbl,0,7,"Volume",   text_color=color.silver, text_size=size.tiny)
    table.cell(tbl,1,7,d_vol,      text_color=color.aqua,   text_size=size.tiny)
    table.cell(tbl,0,8,"Sweep",    text_color=color.silver, text_size=size.tiny)
    table.cell(tbl,1,8,d_swp,      text_color=color.aqua,   text_size=size.tiny)
    table.cell(tbl,0,9,"Entry",    text_color=color.white,  text_size=size.tiny, bgcolor=color.new(color.teal,55))
    table.cell(tbl,1,9,d_ent,      text_color=(long_armed?color.lime:short_armed?color.red:color.gray), text_size=size.tiny, bgcolor=color.new(color.teal,55))
    table.cell(tbl,0,10,"Size",    text_color=color.silver, text_size=size.tiny)
    table.cell(tbl,1,10,d_sz,      text_color=color.aqua,   text_size=size.tiny)
    table.cell(tbl,0,11,"Session", text_color=color.silver, text_size=size.tiny)
    table.cell(tbl,1,11,d_sess,    text_color=c_sess,       text_size=size.tiny)
    table.cell(tbl,0,12,"Circuit", text_color=color.silver, text_size=size.tiny)
    table.cell(tbl,1,12,d_cb,      text_color=c_cb,         text_size=size.tiny)
    table.cell(tbl,0,13,"Date",    text_color=color.silver, text_size=size.tiny)
    table.cell(tbl,1,13,str.format_time(time, "MMM-dd HH:mm", sess_tz), text_color=color.aqua, text_size=size.tiny)
    table.cell(tbl,0,14,"HTF",     text_color=color.silver, text_size=size.tiny)
    table.cell(tbl,1,14,htf_state, text_color=sig_htf_bull?color.lime:sig_htf_bear?color.red:color.gray, text_size=size.tiny)
